18.18: yia xij pun taub trug waag myenb Navq meib nx, yem ninb Bua Eei kxb yrud Bu'Dovj Zwrtq taaib. yia xij kxvq Eei waag yia Jiu pun ninb. ninb zyrug zweib yetq zweib Eeig trug yia Buaj ninb Eei yetg zuvq waag pun ninb Bua mwavj.
18.8: maiq kunq ninb maaig ninb Eei Jaab tivb tu'q Eaanb mq paag ninb Eang Eei hopq Eei xij zu'g tu'q Zauj uaq teij le-wi myenb fib Bua'g.
18.3: pc'g fivj fovg hxg ziag Eei scvb Kuq maiq kunq vovb kruq fai pa'ki yuvb, xij zu'g zx'q puab zwib Zauj i puv Kamb pwi Zauj ka'sia xq pun sai myenb.
18.21: Riaj meib Bua yem Hruq Namq, “yia Bua Navq haiq nx haib zia'q tu'q myenb trug Eei waag se maiq zeid zyruq kxvq Eei waag?”
18.14: meib Bua xij zung Zwrtq uaq teij fivb fivj myenb se mwavj Jrub Zim Zauj mavg mcvg Eei myenb. mq paag meib Bua c'q, zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, maiq pun meib Bua Navq uaq teij myenb nx zruj.
18.6: sij kxvq haiq taub le-wi myenb yem i-saa-laa-en Eei haiq nxm zivb maaib Hruq xij mivb zyruq kinq uaq nxm txvj, sweib ninb mivb yaag tu'q.
18.2: ninb Bua maiq tu'q Zauj ninb Bua Eei kxb yrud maaib Ripg Eei pwrng. zyruq penj ninb Bua Ripg Eei pwrng Navq ninb Zauj ninb Bua lcvd Jiaj Eei waag nx.
18.20: mq paag sij kxvq maaib haiq taub trug waag myenb tevq yia Eei Buaj trug tovb yia maiq Buaj ninb Eei waag, fai tevq kanb taub zyenb Eei Buaj trug waag, uaq taub zuvq xij zu'g taig.”
18.7: ninb zyrug tevq zyruq, ninb Eei Tinb huvb Eei Buaj fub suj, Navq Zauj ninb Jwavg fivj Eei le-wi myenb yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen fub suj uaq nx.
18.19: haiq taub maiq mwavj naaiq taub trug waag myenb tevq yia Eei Buaj trug Eei waag, yia kanb zyrug tivg uaq taub Eei zwid.
18.17: zyruq kxvq Buaj yia, “ninb Bua Navq naaiq kxvq se lovj Eei.
18.11: puvj tiv puvj Jyemj, kaanq hei, Bruq kwaaj fai Bruq fin.
18.5: weig zu'g zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, yem meib Bua fivb fivj Bu'Dovj kinq ninb Bua Zauj ninb Bua Eei zeib fun taaib sruq Jyenq tevq zyruq Eei Buaj yetg liud fub suj.
18.9: meib Bua tu'q pia'g zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Zeij pun Eei teib puv, maiq tuvq zwrtg yem uaq Eei fivb fivj myenb zruj yruj haig, kamb Riaq haig Eei sig.
18.16: se Navq yem ho-lepq Bov meib Bua Toq zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb. meib Bua kxvq, “maiq tuvq pun yia Bua cvj haid zyruq, yia Bua Eei Tinb huvb Eei Qiaj. yaag maiq tuvq pun yia Bua cvj pwatg naaiq kwaaj tomb trud. maiq zei c'q, Riaj yia Bua zu'g taig.”
18.4: xij zu'g txb meib Bua Eei taaub Txvj laavb zi'g, syavb a'vung tiuq Zauj ka'lanq yrub, Zauj meib Bua Eei taaub paan pa'ki yuvb pyei Jiu pun ninb Bua,
18.10: maiq tuvq pun meib Bua Eei haiq taub myenb zx'q ninb Bua Eei txn fai sia'q zruj puaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq. yem meib Bua ka'Euad yaag maiq tuvq pun haiq taub Jrub Zim, mavg mcvg, zruj faatq,
18.22: sij kxvq trug waag myenb tevq zyruq Eei Buaj trug waag, Zwrtq taaib Eei sig yaag maiq txij ninb trug Eei waag, uaq teij waag maiq zeid zyruq kxvq Eei waag. uaq taub trug waag myenb kanb Namq Zwrtq taaib kxvq Navq. maiq tuvq kamb Riaj ninb.
18.12: ta'faanb zruj naaiq Euvg sig Eei myenb, zyruq yruj haig. laaij zruj naaiq Euvg sig, zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, zung ninb Bua Zwrtq meib Bua Eei uaq Daavg mcvj.
18.15: zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, xij pun taub trug waag myenb Navq yia nx, yem meib Bua Eei kxb yrud Bu'Dovj Zwrtq taaib. meib Bua xij zu'g mwavj ninb Eei waag.
18.13: meib Bua xij zu'g yem zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb Eei Ra'Myen, zruj maiq maaib txvj Gemb Eei myenb.
18.1: zruj sai Eei le-wi myenb Zauj le-wi fivj Eei yetg zuvq myenb yem i-saa-laa-en myenb ka'Euad maiq maaib ninb Bua Eei pwrng yaag maiq tu'q Ripg haiq Euvg. ninb Bua Eang Eei, hopq Eei, se myenb fovg hxg puaq ziag pun zyruq Eei ka'naaiq. naaiq se ninb Bua hxpg zu'g tu'q Eei pwrng.

8.18: xij zu'g Javj Jyenq zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, pun meib Bua maaib panb zeig Navq naaiq nx putq zxib taaib, weig zyepg zua'q Eei ei Jyenq ninb Zauj meib Bua Eei ovb Taaij hruq Jyenq lyepg Eei vcvg waag Navq ib Nxi nx.
8.3: ninb pun meib Bua Eyemg kanb zruj faij, pun meib Bua Hruq sia, cvj zx'q maa-naa pun meib Bua Eang, tovb meib Bua kanb fai meib Bua Eei ovb Taaij maiq hiuq Eei ka'naaiq. naaiq se weig pun meib Bua hiuq tu'q myenb maiq zeid Kuvj Kauj Eang hopq yuvd mcvg Navq. yaag xij zu'g Kauj zyruq kxvq Eei Jrub Jruj waag.
8.8: uaq nxm teib puv yaag maaib Byaub witq Zauj Byaub Baa-li, maaib a'vung Mei, vovb Exj Dyavj, zi'g lyrub Dyavj, ka'lanq Dyavj Zauj mweib txvb.
8.19: ib Nxi yia xij Niab Niaq Eei Kwinj meib Bua. sij kxvq meib Bua la'Ku'q zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, mivb pua'g zavg paaij kanb taub zyenb nx, meib Bua Dovg haaij zuvq xij zu'g myetg.
8.9: yem uaq nxm teib puv meib Bua yaag maiq vxg, maiq Zaa haiq Euvg. uaq teij Dau Eei la'pyeiq maaib Lia'q. yem uaq Bov yaag haib wetq Zwrtq tovb si'q.
8.7: weig zu'g zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, xij txb meib Bua pia'g nxm lovj haig Eei teib puv. uaq nxm teib puv maaib Do'q, maaib uamb zivq, uamb Beuj yem uaq hxvd yaag yem uaq Bov lyrug Zwrtq.
8.5: yem meib Bua Eei Hruq xij zu'g hiuq tu'q zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Bx'q Faauj meib Bua Navq tia Bx'q Faauj kanb Eei txn nx.
8.16: yem uaq teib puvb Waav ninb pun maa-naa meib Bua Eang, se tovb meib Bua Eei ovb Taaij maiq hiuq Eei ka'naaiq. naaiq se weig pun meib Bua Eyemg kanb zruj faij, weig seij meib Bua, pun meib Bua Ga'haaq hivq tu'q lovj.
8.20: Navq zyruq pun yem meib Bua Eei uaq Daavg mcvj uaq teij fivb fivj myenb zu'g myetg, meib Bua yaag Navq uaq nx zu'g myetg laaij maiq mwavj zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb Eei waag.
8.17: xij zu'g faij fim, maiq tuvq yem Hruq Namq, “se yia kanb Eei Qa'q, yia kanb Eei panb zeig pun yia Navq naaiq nx putq zxib.”
8.14: Riaj meib Bua Eei Hruq zruj mauj, la'Ku'q zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, tovb txb meib Bua Zwrtq i-yipq teib puv, zruj nrub Eei txvj.
8.4: naaiq teij feij zyepg Havj ka'Euad meib Bua Eei lwib hruj maiq huq, zauj yaag maiq omj.
8.2: meib Bua xij zu'g Javj Jyenq yem uaq teib puvb Waav naaiq teij feij zyepg Havj ka'Euad, zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Navq haiq nx txb meib Bua, weig pun meib Bua Eyemg kanb zruj faij, weig seij mavg kaaj meib Bua Eei Hruq Navq haiq nx, meib Bua za'kevb kan lovj ninb Eei leib latg zeid fai maiq zeid.
8.6: Navq naaig, meib Bua xij zu'g kan lovj zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb Eei leib latg, yaag yavb ninb Eei tob leid, Taaib ninb.
8.13: meib Bua Eei vovb kwanb, pa'ki yuvb Zauj yuvb kwanb Yaavj Jyenq faauj, meib Bua Eei Jyem Eaanb Zauj maaib Eei Euvb Euvg ka'naaiq yaag Zamq Jyenq faauj uaq zang,
8.12: maiq zei c'q, meib Bua tu'q Eang peuq, zruj pyauq lovj yem Jyenq Eei zyavb hog,
8.15: zyruq txb meib Bua Jiaj kamb Riaj haig Eei tomb teib puvb Waav. yem uaq maaib naavb to'g Zauj zyepg Eeig Daavb, yaag penj teib puvb haand, maiq maaib uam. ninb pun uam yem la'pyeib vcvg Zwrtq taaib pun meib Bua hopq.
8.11: xij zu'g faij fim, maiq tuvq la'Ku'q zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb. maiq tuvq puvj Dxtq yetg tiub ninb Eei leib latg Zauj livg Zauj leid, tovb yia ib Nxi Jiu pun meib Bua Eei leid.
8.1: xij zu'g faij fim, ei Jyenq yia ib Nxi Jiu pun meib Bua Eei yetg zuvq leib latg, weig pun meib Bua tu'q zyavb Jyenq yaag Yaavj taaib, tu'q pia'g mivb yem zyruq hruq Jyenq lcvd pun meib Bua Eei ovb Taaij uaq nxm teib puv.
8.10: meib Bua tu'q Eang peuq, xij zu'g Zev zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, weig ninb zx'q lovj haig Eei teib puv Jiu pun meib Bua.

33.18: ninb Navq naaiq nx kxvq Tauj sej-Bu-lun fivj, “sej-Bu-lun fivj aag, meib Bua Zwrtq mivb xij zu'g Fyenb yrub. itg-saaj-Kaa fivj aag, yem meib Eei Dopg liub ka'Euad xij zu'g xnb lx'g.
33.8: mo-se Navq naaiq nx kxvq Tauj le-wi fivj, “zyruq aag, meib Eei u-lim Zauj Tum-mim Zauj kan lovj Tinb huvb Eei myenb yem. yem matq-saaj meib seij liud ninb Bua. yem me-li-Baa uam meib tu'q Zauj ninb Bua txib tekg.
33.3: ninb za'kevb Namq ninb Eei pc'g fivj. zwavj Zivb Revg myenb yem ninb Eei puad ka'Euad, ninb Bua yetg zuvq kweig Fiag meib Eei zaub Len zipq meib Paaiq Eei waag.
33.21: ninb Bua weig kanb kinq kaub lovj Jiaj Eei Dau, se lyrub pun pyeiq zeiq hxpg zu'g tu'q Eei pwrng. i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei zwavj pyeiq zeiq kapq zunq Eei zyavb hog, ninb Bua ziuj zyruq Eei eij zruj, yaag ei Jyenq ninb pcvb fim Eei leid.”
33.14: yaag tu'q Ba'Nxi Eei Eutg Tevj ka'naaib zwavj lovj, tu'q Laab Eutg yuvd kcvb zwavj puvb zua'g.
33.23: ninb Navq naaiq nx kxvq Tauj napq-Taa-li fivj, “o napq-Taa-li fivj aag, meib Bua tu'q zyruq Zamb Zamq Eei Zeij en, yaag tu'q ninb Eei fu'q pwavq Revg. ninb Bua Ripg Eei teib puv yem fai puv Zauj naamb puv mcvj.”
33.6: mo-se Navq naaiq nx kxvq Tauj lu-Ben fivj, “Toq pun lu-Ben fivj tu'q zyavb Jyenq maiq taig, yaag maiq tuvq pun ninb Bua Eei myenb zo'g.”
33.2: ninb kxvq, “zyruq yem si-naai Bov taaib, yaag Navq Ba'Nxi yem sej-i faauj taaib cvq ninb Bua. ninb yem paa-laan Bov ziuj Fav Zwrtq taaib. yem Zinb Zin waanb waang Zivb Revg Eei uaq teij taaib, yem ninb Eei Byaaug Jia'q puad maaib zia'g Jyenq Eei trud.
33.20: mo-se yaag Navq naaiq nx kxvq Tauj kaatg fivj, “Zev zyruq, tovb Tevj kaatg fivj Eei teig Javq uaq taub. kaatg Baapq Fiag Navq syenb, zuaq Jyenq petq ka'naaiq Eei puab zwib fai mGxvb pcvb.
33.24: ninb Navq naaiq nx kxvq Tauj aa-se fivj, “aa-se fivj tu'q fu'q kaub Zamq zwavj muab txig, yaag tu'q ninb Bua Eei kxb yrud a'Neiq ninb kaub Zamq, yaag pun ninb Bua Eei teib puv zwavj ka'lanq pyruq kitq.
33.28: Navq naaiq nx, i-saa-laa-en zyrug pcvb xn Eei yem. yaa-Kopq Eei zeib fun tu'q kanb yem Navq, yem nxm maaib Byaub Meiq Zauj syavb a'vung tiuq Eei teib puv, maaib yem luvb Fiag Eei Byuvb swiq yuvd Dau.
33.7: mo-se Navq naaiq nx kxvq Tauj yu-Daa fivj, “o zyruq aag, Toq mwavj yu-Daa fivj Eei Qiaj, Toq txb ninb Bua pia'g taaib Jwavg uaq teij fivj. ninb Bua lovg kanb Eei puad weig kanb Bx'q Jaaj. Toq Tevj ninb Bua Bx'q hivb ninb Bua Eei winb wavq.”
33.29: o i-saa-laa-en myenb aag, meib Bua za'kevb xnb lx'g haig. maaib haiq taub Navq meib Bua penj yetg fivj tu'q zyruq Fruj Eei myenb? ninb zruj meib Bua Eei Txvb paaib Tevj meib Bua, yaag zruj meib Bua Eei Ru'g Daauq pun meib Bua tu'q hivb. meib Bua Eei winb wavq xij taaib Qa'q Toq meib Bua Kxb lyenb, meib Bua zyrug Zaaiq Jyenq ninb Bua yem Lav zavg zyenb Eei txvj.”
33.19: ninb Bua xij heug fivb fivj myenb taaib kapq zunq uaq Bov, yaag yem uaq fovg hxg hxpg zu'g ziag Eei ka'naaiq. ninb Bua xij pavg Kxiq tu'q Kub yem Kub Eang, yaag pavg yem saab zyru ka'Euad tu'q taaib Eei ka'naaiq.”
33.17: yo-sepq henq Navq taub taaub Txi vovb kruq. ninb Eei Jxv Navq Yiab vovb Eei Jxv, ninb xij lovg ninb Eei Jxv Zeuj maang fivj, zung fivb fivj Tauj Jomg luvb Diaq. ninb Eei Jxv se e-faa-im Eei waanb waang myenb, yaag zruj maa-natq-sej Eei Zinb Zin.”
33.27: yetg liud Eei Tinb huvb se meib yem Eei txvj. ninb yetg liud Eei puad prub Jyenq meib. ninb xij zung meib Eei winb wavq Zwrtq meib Eei uaq Daavg mcvj, yaag kxvq, ‘myetg ninb maa'b!’
33.11: o zyruq aag, Toq Zeij fu'q pun ninb Bua maaib Eei ka'naaiq, yaag a'Neiq ninb Bua Eei puad zruj Eei kov. Toq vatq ninb Bua Eei winb wavq, pun Rxv ninb Bua uaq teij maiq haib cvj henq Jiad taaib.”
33.5: pc'g fivj Eei pyeiq zeiq kapq zunq Eei zyavb hog, fivb fivj i-saa-laa-en myenb yaag taaib Rxib,   zyruq zruj ye-su-lun Eei huvb tiaj.
33.9: le-wi kxvq Tauj kanb Eei tiaj maag. ninb kxvq, ‘yia maiq hiuq tu'q ninb Bua a'q.’ ninb maiq Javj ninb Eei muab txig, yaag maiq Eyemg ninb kanb Eei naamb Erud. weig zu'g ninb kan lovj meib Eei livg, yaag zyepg zua'q Eei ei Jyenq meib Zauj ninb lcvd Jiaj Eei vcvg waag.
33.16: tu'q paamb ken maaib Eei yetg zuvq kaub lovj Jiaj Eei ka'naaiq. yaag tu'q yem zia'g Jyenq Eei Dyavb txnb fomq uaq taub a'Neiq ninb Bua. Toq pun naaiq teij fu'q yetg zuvq Fiag Tauj yo-sepq Eei zeib fun Eei mGxvq, se Fiag Tauj yem ninb Eei kxb yrud Bu'Dovj zruj pyeiq zeiq uaq taub Eei mGxvb pcvb.
33.4: mo-se zx'q leib latg Jiu pun Bua, penj yaa-Kopq Eei zeib fun Ripg Eei pwrng.
33.10: le-wi fivj txb meib Eei leid Faauj yaa-Kopq, yaag txb meib Eei leib latg Faauj i-saa-laa-en myenb. ninb Bua zx'q huv an meib Eei Ra'Myen, yaag zx'q zyavb taub puaq Eei scvb Kuq an meib Eei ziab txvb.
33.22: mo-se Navq naaiq nx kxvq Tauj Daan fivj, “Daan fivj se Navq taub syenb txn, yem Baa-saan teig piu Zwrtq taaib.”
33.12: mo-se Navq naaiq kxvq Tauj Ben-yaa-min fivj, “zyruq Namq Eei myenb tu'q Kauj ninb pcvb xn Eei yem, weig zu'g ninb zyavb Nxi zyavb mwrnd Ria Jyenq ninb Bua, yaag yem ninb Bua Bu'Dovj.”
33.15: tu'q lob Nxi Eei Bov Zwrtq kaub lovj Jiaj Eei ka'naaiq, Zauj yetg liud yem Eei Bovb aiq zyavb kaub lovj Jiaj Eei pwrng.
33.13: ninb yaag Navq naaiq nx kxvq Tauj yo-sepq Eei zeib fun, “Toq zyruq Zeij fu'q pun ninb Bua Eei Dau, tu'q luvb zavg Eei Byuvb swiq, yaag tu'q Daub Diaq Eei uam saamj Zwrtq.
33.1: naaiq se Tinb huvb Eei myenb, mo-se, maiq kcvb kwei seij uaq zang pwav waag pun i-saa-laa-en myenb.
33.26: “maiq maaib haiq taub haib peiq tu'q Tauj ye-su-lun Eei Tinb huvb. ninb keb Jyenq Bwrnj taaib Tevj meib, ninb maaib haavb taaub Eei Favb laavg Jiaj luvb taaib.
33.25: meib Bua Eei laatg kcvb Eei sxn lovg Lia'q Zauj tovb si'q zruj taaib. meib Bua Eei Qa'q xij Pwij meib Bua Eei Nxib Eia'g.

3.18: uaq zang yia Paaiq meib Bua, kxvq, “zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, zx'q naaiq nxm teib puv Jiu pun meib Bua, penj meib Bua Eei pwrng. meib Bua Eei yetg zuvq Bx'q Jaaj henq Eei myenb xij zu'g pwij Jyenq ua'g king yem meib Bua Eei i-saa-laa-en myenb kxb yrud Eei uaq Daavg mcvj Jiaj Jx-Dcn Daaib.
3.8: uaq zang Bua Zaavq Revg aa-mo-lai myenb Eei i taub huvb Eei teib puv yem Jx-Dcn Daaib Eei tov puv mcvj, aan-non hxvd, mivb Tauj he-mon Bov.
3.3: zyruq, Bua Eei Tinb huvb, yaag zx'q Baa-saan Eei okg huvb, Zauj ninb Eei zwavj pcv Jiu pun yem Bua Eei puab Diaq. Bua zyrug taij Revg ninb Bua. maiq lyrub yetg taub.
3.21: uaq zang yia Buaj yo-su-waa, “meib kanb Eei mziv tu'q pwatg zyruq, meib Eei Tinb huvb, Navq haiq nx zruj pun naaiq teij i taub huvb. zyruq yaag xij Navq uaq nx zruj pun tovb Jiaj uaq vaang meib Bua xij mivb Eei nxmb nxm teib puv.
3.14: maaib taub maa-natq-sej Eei zeib fun, Jaa-i, Zaavq tu'q aan-kopg teig yetg zuvq, se Baa-saan teib puv mivb Tauj ke-su myenb Zauj maa-aa-Kaa myenb Eei kapg Jaaij. ninb Zwrtq uaq nxm txvj Eei laavd Eei Buaj heug nitq ninb kanb Eei Buaj. Baa-saan teib puv Zxg maaib Buaj heug haau-wotq-Jaa-i Navq ib Jaaj Nxi nx.)
3.23: uaq zang yia Qa'q Toq zyruq,
3.6: Bua yaag myetg Revg ninb Bua Navq Bua zruj pun hetq-Bon zivb Eei si-honj huvb uaq nx, se myetg Revg nxmb nxm zivb, lyemb mJavg msia'q Zauj fu'Jweiq.
3.2: zyruq kxvq Buaj yia, “maiq tuvq kamb Riaj ninb, weig zu'g yia zx'q ninb Zauj ninb Eei zwavj pcv Zauj ninb Eei teib puv Jiu pun yem meib Bua Eei puab Diaq mig a'q. xij zu'g zruj pun ninb Navq meib Bua zruj pun yem hetq-Bon uaq taub aa-mo-lai myenb Eei huvb, si-honj, uaq nx.”
3.20: zuaq meib Bua Eei kxb yrud tu'q hitq Kwrnj Navq meib Bua nx. se zuaq ninb Bua tu'q yem Jyenq uaq vaang puv Jx-Dcn Daaib, tovb zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Jiu pun ninb Bua Eei teib puv. Ga'haaq meib Bua kx'g myenb tu'q Rwrnj yia Zeij pun kx'g myenb Eei pwrng Dau.”
3.24: “o zyruq Tinb huvb aag, meib pun yia, meib Eei pru, Jiad kxn pwatg meib henq haig Eei tomb Qa'q. yem luvb yem Dau maaib haiq taub zyenb haib Navq zyruq zruj Lo haig, henq haig Eei sig?
3.28: xij zu'g Paaiq yo-su-waa, Kwinj ninb, Tevj ninb zuvj Qa'q, weig zu'g ninb xij zu'g txb naaiq teij myenb Jiaj Daaib Ripg meib tu'q pwatg Eei teib puv.”
3.7: mq paag yetg zuvq scvb Kuq Zauj yem zivb Zaavq taaib Eei ka'naaiq Bua txb mivb lyrub Bua kanb lovg.
3.29: Navq naaig, Bua yem Jyenq Betg-pe-o zivb txib vaang Eei hxvd.
3.19: mq paag meib Bua Eei aub Jweiq Zauj meib Bua Eei scvb Kuq, (yia hiuq tu'q meib Bua maaib scvb Kuq Zamq haig), xij zu'g yem yia Jiu pun meib Bua liud uaq teij zivb,
3.17: fai puv Eei kapg Jaaij yem aa-laa-Baa Eei Jx-Dcn Daaib, se yem Kin-ne-letq Kxib txn mivb Tauj aa-laa-Baa Kxiq, se Kxib Rauq, pitg-kaa Eei Bovb Jua'q.
3.27: meib faauj pitg-kaa Bovb nivq mivb mavg tov naamb fai pa'q. lovg meib kanb Eei mziv mavg uaq nxm teib puv weig zu'g meib zuvq maiq tu'q Jiaj Jx-Dcn Daaib.
3.11: (zevg Fiag Eei le-faa-im myenb Kuvj maaib Baa-saan Eei okg huvb Navq. ninb Eei Zruj lovg Lia'q zruj taaib, Daauq Duab Dx'g, Javq pyei Dx'g, ziuj Prub Tov Eei Dx'g. naaiq zuv Zruj ib Jaaj Nxi Zxg yem am-mon myenb Eei lapq-Baa zivb.)
3.5: naaiq teij yetg zuvq zivb maaib zivb laatg Lav, maaib laatg kcvb, yaag maaib kcvb sxn Tevj zivb wrnq. maiq maaib zivb laatg Eei laavd yaag maaib Zamq Eei.
3.9: (naaiq nxm he-mon Bov, sai-Dxn myenb heug sij-li-xn. aa-mo-lai myenb heug sej-ni.)
3.16: yem aan-non hxvd, lovg hxvd Bu'Dovj zruj kapg Jaaij, mivb Tauj am-mon myenb Eei kapg Jaaij, yapq-Bxkg Daaib, yia pun Revg lu-Ben fivj Zauj kaatg fivj.
3.4: uaq zang Bua zx'q Revg ninb Eei yetg zuvq zivb. yem Baa-saan Eei okg huvb kunq Eei aan-kopg teig, Bua zx'q Revg lua'g zyepg nxm zivb. maiq maaib yetg nxm zivb Bua maiq tu'q zx'q.
3.10: Bua Zaavq tu'q Revg lamb Lav Daub pcvb Eei nxmb nxm zivb Zauj ki-le-aatg teig yetg zuvq Zauj Baa-saan teig yetg zuvq, mivb Tauj saaj-le-Kaa Zauj e-Den-i zivb. naaiq se Baa-saan kua'q Eei okg huvb Eei zivb.
3.22: maiq tuvq kamb Riaj ninb Bua weig zu'g zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb kanb, xij weig meib Bua Bx'q Jaaj.”
3.12: uaq zang Bua Zaavq tu'q taaib Eei teib puv yem aan-non hxvd ka'Len Eei aa-lo-e zivb pa'q puv, lyemb ki-le-aatg Eei yetg pwrng Bov zavg txvj Zauj uaq teij teib puv Eei zivb Jiu pun lu-Ben fivj Zauj kaatg fivj.
3.15: yia zx'q ki-le-aatg teig pun taub maa-natq-sej Eei zeib fun, maa-Ki-le.
3.13: ki-le-aatg zevg Fiag Eei Dau Zauj okg huvb Eei kua'q, Baa-saan, se aan-kopg teig yetg zuvq, yia Jiu pun maa-natq-sej Daamb fivj. (Baa-saan teig myenb heug zruj le-faa-im myenb Eei teig.
3.1: Ga'haaq Bua Win huvj Jyenq Baa-saan mivb. Baa-saan teig Eei okg huvb, Zauj ninb Eei zwavj pcv zyrug Zwrtq taaib Tauj e-Den-i zivb Zauj Bua Bx'q Jaaj.
3.26: mq paag laaij meib Bua, zyruq Qiaj Jiad yia, maiq mwavj yia. zyruq kxvq, “kauj a'q! maiq tuvq cvj Zauj yia kxvq naaiq teij sig maa'b!
3.25: Toq Gxi Rwib pun yia Jiaj uaq vaang zi'g Jx-Dcn Daaib mavg uaq nxm lovj haig Eei teib puv, se uaq nxm Rweig haig Eei keb zxv, Zauj le-Baa-nxn keb.”

32.18: meib Bua maiq Javj pun meib Bua Zwrtq seij uaq taub, yaag la'Ku'q yuvd meib Bua taaib uaq taub Tinb huvb.
32.45: kxvq liud naaiq teij yetg zuvq waag pun i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb mwavj uaq zang,
32.3: yia xij zunb zyruq Eei mevb, xij zu'g Zev Bua Eei Tinb huvb weib Lo.
32.43: o maang kua'q myenb aag, xij zu'g Zauj Tinb huvb Eei pc'g fivj Fyenb yrub, weig zu'g ninb xij weig ninb Eei pru Eei Ryaamq Jaauq win. ninb xij Jaauq ninb Eei winb wavq Eei syrub, xij fi'q ninb Eei teib puv, kwavg ninb Eei myenb Eei zwid.
32.50: meib zuvq xij zu'g yem meib faauj uaq nxm Bov kwei seij, Navq meib Eei kxj, aa-lon, yem ho-aa Bov kwei seij mig a'q,
32.14: ninb pun vovb Exb Mei Zauj yuvb Exj, pa'ki yuvb txn Zauj yuvb kruq Jung, se Baa-saan teig kaub lovj Jiaj Eei yuvb. ninb Bua tu'q Eang zavg hxvb Eei Byaub witq, tu'q hopq a'vung pyruq kaub lovj Jiaj Eei tiuq.
32.48: tovb uaq Nxi zyruq kxvq Buaj mo-se,
32.34: “yia syru Jyenq winb wavq zruj Eei naaiq teij sig, Bx'q Jyenq yenj yia syru Jaaij Eei ka'naaiq Eei txvj maiq zeid?
32.2: pun yia Faauj Eei leid Navq twib Byuvg Fiag nx, yia kxvq Eei waag Fiag Navq Byuvb swiq Fiag, Navq Byuvb Bwrnq Fiag miab lunj, yaag Navq Byuvb kxv lyemb miab Eyemd.
32.36: zyruq pwatg ninb Eei pc'g fivj Eei Qa'q Revg. maiq zevg yetg taub maiq kunq zruj nrub fai maiq zruj nrub Eei. ninb zyrug Fruj ninb Eei pc'g fivj, yaag Kxb lyenb ninb Eei pru.
32.35: Jaauq win se yem yia. yia za'kevb Jaauq a'q. zuaq ninb Bua Eei zauj Zaaiq Pyatq Dxpg mig a'q. ninb Bua zu'g ze'g naang Eei Nxib Eia'g Tauj fatq a'q. zu'g myetg Eei zyavb hog xij syepg syepq Eei Tauj.”
32.24: pun ninb Bua pwavb tomb vxg zyrug Kxv Jaig Eei, zu'g to'g haig Eei pcvg, sin Lu'q Jxm Eei, yaag putq Zyruq haig Eei wrnb pcvg myetg ninb Bua. yia xij pun Yiab zxib Eei Eaab vaatg ninb Bua. pun lwib kan niab Buv Eei naavb to'g Ex'q.
32.7: meib Bua xij zu'g Javj Tauj lob Nxi, Namq Tauj Jiaj taaib ziaj txig Eei Havb taaub. naaig meib Bua Eei tia, ninb zyrug pun meib Bua hiuq. naaig meib Bua Eei myenb koj, ninb Bua zyrug Buaj meib Bua.
32.17: ninb Bua ziag myenq, tovb maiq zeid zyen zyenb. zavg zinb Daavg maiq hiuq tu'q Eei zyenb, zavg Zo'q ho'g Zwrtq taaib syav Eei zyenb. zavg meib Bua Eei ovb Taaij maiq zavg Jiaj Eei zyenb.
32.49: “meib xij zu'g faauj aa-Baa-lim keb zxv Tauj mo-apg teib puv Eei ne-Bo Bov, yem ye-li-Ko zivb txib vaang, mavg tovb yia xij Jiu pun i-saa-laa-en myenb weig penj ninb Bua Ripg Eei pwrng uaq nxm Kaa-naa-an teib puv.
32.11: Navq tomb Jaavq Faauj txn Daij, lovg Daatq Ria Jyenq ninb Eei txn. ninb yav Daatq Faauj ninb Eei txn ho'g, Tauj txn Eei Daatq henq, haib Daij faauj,
32.33: ninb Bua Eei a'vung tiuq se naav Eei Diab to'g, naavb Jia'q Zyruq haig Eei to'g Qiaj.
32.16: ninb Bua zavg kanb fivj myenb Eei zyenb pun Tinb huvb hang ninb Bua. ninb Bua zruj yruj haig, kamb Riaq haig Eei sig, Zua'q ninb Qiaj Jiad.
32.40: yia suv puad zyavq luvb hruq Jyenq kxvq, Navq yia yetg liud zyavb Jyenq, Dovg uaq zyen,
32.37: ninb zyrug kxvq, “ninb Bua Eei zyenb yem haaij? ninb Bua Kauj uaq taub zyruq ni?
32.4: ninb se peu Bua uaq taub zyruq, ninb zruj Eei kov tunb yunb Revg. ninb zruj Eei Jauq yetg zuvq pcvb fim Eei. ninb se zyepg zua'q Eei Tinb huvb, maiq zruj txvg haiq Euvg. ninb pcvb fim Eei, yaag zruj tu'q hxpg.
32.51: weig zu'g meib Bua i muad yem sinj teib puvb Waav, Kaa-Detg teig Eei me-li-Baa uam zruj txvg yia, tovb meib Bua txv Jyenq i-saa-laa-en myenb maiq Taaib yia Zivb Revg.
32.12: zyruq kanb Du'g taub txb ninb Eei pc'g fivj, maiq maaib kanb fivj Eei zyenb Zauj ninb Bua yem.
32.46: mo-se kxvq Buaj ninb Bua, “xij zu'g lovg Hruq Javj Jyenq yia ib Nxi kxvq pun meib Bua mwavj Eei yetg zuvq waag. Navq naaig meib Bua haib hatg meib Bua Eei txnb Jweiq funb fa'q lovb lovj Eei ei Jyenq naaiq teij leib latg Eei yetg zuvq waag.
32.13: ninb pun ninb Bua kunq Daub peib Lav Eei txvj, tu'q Eang yem Deig Zwrtq Eei kcvb zwavj, pun ninb Bua tu'q Eang yem la'pyeiq ka'Euad Eei mweib txvb, yaag Eang yem la'pyeib Dau Zwrtq Eei ka'lanq yrub.
32.26: yia kxvq yia xij pun ninb Bua faatq Raanj, pun ninb Bua Eei Buaj yem maang myenb Bu'Dovj zutg Revg.
32.28: i-saa-laa-en myenb maiq Kavq ei Jyenq Zaavb laavb liud Eei waag zruj, ninb Bua maiq pia'g Hruq haiq Euvg.
32.8: yem Lav Jiaj uaq taub Jiu pun maang fivj Ripg ninb Bua Eei pwrng, zx'q paamb myenb pun Gxi Eei zyavb hog, ziuj i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei sruj mrug, ninb tivg maang fivj Eei kapg Jaaij,
32.9: weig zu'g zyruq Eei pwrng se ninb Eei pc'g fivj, ninb kanb Ripg Eei pwrng se yaa-Kopq Eei zeib fun.
32.32: winb wavq se Navq soj-Dom Eei a'vung Mei, yaag Navq ko-mo-laa Eei Deig Eei Mei zyavb Eei. ninb Bua Eei a'vung pyruq maaib to'g Qiaj, ninb Bua Eei a'vung pyrub Jxib yaag im.
32.21: ninb Bua zavg tovb maiq zeid zyen zyenb, pun yia hang ninb Bua. ninb Bua paaij maiq lamb lovg Eei miub favj Zua'q yia Qiaj Jiad. yia zyrug lovg maiq maaib kua'q Eei myenb pun ninb Bua mweig Jia'q, lovg yetg fivj Vovj Eei myenb Zua'q ninb Bua Qiaj Jiad.
32.23: “yia xij zx'q ziaj Euvg ze'g naang Dwi Jyenq ninb Bua, puvj Revg yia Eei fxvb Zav taaib pwrnq ninb Bua.
32.6: o meib Bua Vovj haig, maiq maaib Zovb mevb Eei myenb aa'b! meib Bua Navq naaiq winb pun zyruq? ninb zruj meib Bua Eei tia, zeij meib Bua, lyepg meib Bua taaib yaag yuvd meib Bua maiq zeid?
32.44: mo-se Zauj nun Eei txn, yo-su-waa, taaib kxvq Revg naaiq tiub Ruv Eei waag pun pc'g fivj mwavj.
32.20: ninb kxvq, “yia xij pwav Jyenq yia Eei Myen, maiq mavg ninb Bua. yia xij zuaq Jyenq mavg kaaj, Tauj setq mweid ninb Bua Navq haiq nx. ninb Bua se yetg txig tu'g eij maiq mwavj waag Eei myenb, penj maiq zyepg zua'q Eei naamb Erud.
32.5: ninb Bua maiq zyepg zua'q Eei zruj pun ninb, ninb Bua maaib txvj Gemb, maiq tu'q zruj ninb Eei naamb Erud a'q, penj yetg txig Hruq vau Hruq Fwrtq Eei myenb.
32.19: zyruq mavg zyrug Gemb ninb Bua, laaij ninb Eei naamb Erud zruj pun ninb Qiaj Jiad.
32.38: tovb Eang ninb Bua ziag uaq teij xb Jung, yaag hopq ninb Bua Ziaq ziag Eei a'vung tiuq. pun uaq teij zyenb taaib Tevj meib Bua, pun ninb Bua peu Jyenq meib Bua maa'b!
32.31: yia Bua Eei winb wavq hiuq tu'q kanb Eei zyenb maiq Navq yia Bua Eei Tinb huvb.
32.52: weig naaiq meib zyrug yem ko Eei mavg yia Jiu pun i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei teib puv mq paag meib maiq tu'q pia'g.”
32.27: mq paag yia kamb Riaj winb wavq puvj waab mauj, Riaj ninb Bua pia'g Hruq txvg. Raub heij winb wavq kxvq, ‘se yia Bua kanb Eei Qa'q tu'q hivb, maiq zeid zyruq zruj naaiq teij yetg zuvq sig.’+”
32.41: sij kxvq yia Ryruj laig Ryruj pc'g yia Eei Ru'g Daauq zcvb zcvb Eei, yia Eei puad nanq Jyenq xij tivg zwid, yia xij Jaauq yia Eei winb wavq Eei syrub, xij winb pun Rxv yia uaq teij.
32.1: o luvb aag, pcv mnxmb mwavj lovj. yia xij kxvq waag. o paamb ken aag, Toq mwavj yem yia Eei Rwib Zwrtq Eei Einb Erud.
32.39: “mavg maa'b! se yia, yia kanb, zruj Tinb huvb. Zwrtq liud yia, maiq maaib kanb taub zyenb. yia pun myenb taig yaag pun myenb navb, yia pun myenb zu'g mun yaag zxg myenb lovj, maiq maaib haiq taub haib zx'q ninb Bua Zwrtq yia Eei puab Diaq.
32.47: naaiq teij waag maiq zeid weig meib Bua penj Kuvb waag, se penj meib Bua Eei mcvg. meib Bua ei Jyenq naaiq teij waag zruj, meib Bua zyrug zyavb tu'q syrug Ewrnb Daauq yem meib Bua xij Jiaj Jx-Dcn Daaib tu'q penj meib Bua Eei pwrng uaq nxm teib puv.”
32.10: zyruq pwavb zu'g ninb Bua yem uaq teib puvb Waav, yem maiq maaib haiq Euvg Eei txvj, Kuvj maaib Ryaauj Eei Qiaj Bwi Navq. ninb Wiv kxmj, Ria Jyenq ninb Bua, Navq kruj kanb Eei mzivb myenb nx.
32.25: yem ka'Eiag maaib Ru'g Daauq taij ninb Bua. yem pyauq ka'Euad yaag kamb Riaj Jyenq. txnb lunj sia'g lunj xij zu'g myetg, lyemb hopq Exj Eei kub vwaad Zauj ovb mGxvb pc'g zu'g myetg Revg.
32.22: yia Qiaj Jiad Navq trud zia'g Jyenq, zuvq zia'g Tauj yemb ken Do Jiaj Eei txvj, xij puaq Revg Daub peib Zauj kcvb zwavj ka'naaiq, zuvq zia'g Tauj Bov Eei kxnb Do'q.
32.42: yia xij pun yia Eei fxvb Zav hopq Ryaamq Gwin, pun yia Eei Ru'g Daauq Eang xq, tovb zu'g Zaavq taaib taij taig uaq teij myenb Eei Ryaamq, Zauj winb wavq pyeiq Eei mGxvq.”
32.15: mq paag ye-su-lun putq zxib taaib, Ga'haaq vcvg  zyruq, ninb Bua Jung, ti'g taand hod, Kub yem Kub Eang, zyrug kwavg zeij ninb Bua taaib uaq taub Tinb huvb, mavg Piaj Fruj ninb Bua uaq taub zyruq.
32.29: feij tu'q ninb Bua maaib Zovb mevb, haib pia'g Hruq naaiq teij sig zyrug samj tu'q Zwrtq ninb Bua setq mweid Eei zyavb hog.
32.30: yetg laanb myenb Navq haiq nx haib zung tu'q yetg Zin laanb? i laanb Navq haiq nx haib zung yetg waang laanb pyauj? Zwrtq liud peu ninb Bua uaq taub zyruq maaig ninb Bua, ninb Bua Eei zyruq yaag leib kwavg ninb Bua.

21.18: haiq taub maaib txn, uaq taub txn maiq zyavb hxvb, Hruq vcvg haig, tiaj maag Bx'q Faauj yaag maiq mwavj,
21.8: o zyruq aag, Toq meib kwavg Gxi meib Eei pc'g fivj, i-saa-laa-en myenb, Eei zwid, se meib zua'g taaib Eei pc'g fivj. Toq maiq tuvq pun meib Eei myenb weig naaiq taub maiq zruj txvg Eei myenb zu'g taij taig Eei zwid Daamb txv.”
21.3: yem nitq Janb taig kaub fatq uaq nxm zivb Eei myenb koj xij zu'g txb taub maiq kcvb zruj Jiaj kov yaag maiq kaad Jiaj Dyavb kaad Eei vovb zeig,
21.21: uaq nxm zivb Eei zwavj mJavg txn zyrug lovg la'pyeiq zov taig ninb. Navq naaig meib Bua zyrug pun yem meib Bua Bu'Dovj maiq maaib naaiq Euvg x'q sig. i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb haid naaiq teij sig zyrug kamb Riaj haig.
21.14: hod taaib sij kxvq maiq pwavq Hruq ninb, pun ninb Zwrtq yaag sweib ninb mivb haaij yaag tu'q. maiq tuvq pun ninb txvj nrub maaig Eaanb, weig zu'g meib paaig zu'g ninb mig a'q.
21.23: maiq tuvq lyrub ninb Eei sei yem uaq Dyavj Jiaj mwrnd. tovb uaq Nxi zuvq xij zu'g pyopq, weig zu'g haiq taub zu'g Diuj Jyenq Dyavj kub vwaaig, uaq taub zu'g Tinb huvb zyruj. maiq tuvq zruj pun zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Jiu pun meib Bua Ripg Eei teib puv maaib wij.
21.6: yem nitq Janb taig kaub fatq uaq nxm zivb Eei myenb koj zyrug yem uaq nxm hxvd, Raauj ninb Bua Eei puad yem Bx'q Jaav nauq uaq taub vovb zeig kub vwaaig.
21.2: xij zu'g heug meib Bua Eei myenb koj Zauj syemq zwid Jyen Zwrtq mivb Dx'g mavg kaaj, naaiq taub zu'g taij Eei myenb yem ninb taig Eei txvj nitq weib kxmj Eei zivb haiq nxm kaub fatq Jiaj.
21.20: ninb Bua xij zu'g kxvq Buaj uaq teij myenb koj, “yia Bua Eei naaiq taub txn Hruq vcvg haig, maiq mwavj yia Bua Eei waag. Kuvj zruj Pa'li Pa'laaij Eei sig mauq Eang hopq Gwin Navq.”
21.7: ninb Bua zyrug zruj zxvb zevj kxvq, “maiq zeid yia Bua Eei puad taij naaiq taub myenb. yia Bua kanb Eei mziv yaag maiq pwatg ninb zu'g taij taig.
21.19: ninb Eei tiaj maag xij zu'g zx'q ninb txb mivb Tauj kanb Eei pwrnb zivb kcvb Daavg, myenb koj uaq.
21.17: ninb xij zu'g pun suvb kruq ka'naaiq tovb ninb maiq Namq uaq taub auq Eei txn weig Eyemg ninb zruj txnb la'kauq. naaiq taub zruj ninb Eei taaub taub txn. zruj txnb la'kauq tu'q suvb kruq Eei leid penj ninb Eei.
21.11: yem Zaavq taaib Eei myenb ka'Euad pwatg maaib sia'q Rweig, yaag haid xij lovg zruj auq,
21.5: le-wi Eei zeib fun uaq teij sai myenb xij zu'g Zwrtq mivb Tauj uaq nxm txvj. zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, kinq ninb Bua taaib fub suj ninb, tevq zyruq Eei Buaj pwav waag yaag tunj yetg zuvq Rcv Jaaj Zauj zruj pun myenb zu'g mun Eei sig.
21.9: Navq naaiq ziuj zyruq pwatg, meib Bua zruj tu'q hxpg zyrug maiq zu'g weig maiq zruj txvg Eei myenb zu'g taij taig Daamb txv.
21.16: Tauj pun Gxi Jaab tivb ninb Eei txn Ripg Eei zyavb hog, maiq tuvq zx'q zruj txnb la'kauq tu'q suvb kruq ka'naaiq pun ninb Namq uaq taub auq Eei txn, Kwei zu'g za'kevb zruj txnb la'kauq uaq taub, tovb ninb maiq Namq uaq taub auq Eei txn.
21.4: mivb Tauj nxm hxvd. uaq nxm hxvd myenb maiq laib Jiaj Dau fai zwavj Jiaj ka'naaiq yaag maaib Do'q, maaib uamb taaib Eei. yem uaq xij zu'g Bx'q vovb Eei Jaav nauq.
21.10: meib Bua Zwrtq mivb Bx'q Jaaj uaq zang, zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Jiu ninb Bua zu'g yem meib Bua Eei puab Diaq, meib Bua zyrug Zaavq tu'q ninb Bua.
21.22: sij kxvq maaib taub myenb paamd zig tu'q taij Eei zwid, ninb zu'g taij taig cvj zx'q sei Diuj Jyenq Dyavj kub vwaaig,

2.35: mq paag scvb Kuq Zauj yem nxmb nxm zivb Zaavq taaib Eei ka'naaiq Bua txb mivb lyrub Jyenq penj Bua kanb Eei.

2.6: meib Bua xij zu'g lovg Eaanb Tevj ninb Bua maaid ka'naaiq Eang, yaag lovg Eaanb Tevj ninb Bua maaid uam hopq.’+”

2.20: (naaiq nxm teib puv se funj penj le-faa-im myenb Eei teib puv weig zu'g zinb Daavg ninb Bua yem Jiaj, mq paag am-mon myenb heug ninb Bua zruj samj-sum-mim myenb.
2.24: zyruq cvj Buaj Bua, “xij zu'g Zwrtq Jauq Jiaj aan-non hxvd. yia zx'q aa-mo-lai myenb, hetq-Bon zivb Eei si-honj huvb, Zauj ninb Eei teib puv Jiu pun meib Bua. meib Bua xij zu'g Jiad kxn Zauj ninb Bua Bx'q Jaaj, Zaavq ninb Bua Eei teib puv.
2.28: Toq maaig ka'naaiq pun yia Bua Eang, maaig uam pun yia Bua hopq, lovg yia Bua Eei Eaanb. yia Bua Kuvj Toq meib pun yia Bua yavb Jauq Jiaj Navq,
2.7: zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Zeij fu'q meib Bua lovg puad zruj Eei Euvb Euvg kov. meib Bua Jiaj tomb teib puvb Waav ninb yaag kruj Jyenq meib Bua. naaiq teij feij zyepg Havj ka'Euad, zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Zauj meib Bua yem. meib Bua yaag maiq Zaa haiq Euvg.
2.29: Navq yem sej-i teig, e-saau Eei zeib fun Zauj yem aan zivb Eei mo-apg myenb pun yia Bua Jiaj uaq nx, Tauj yia Jiaj Jx-Dcn Daaib pia'g zyruq, yia Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Jiu pun yia Bua Eei teib puv.”
2.19: meib Bua Jiaj Tauj am-mon myenb Eei teig maiq tuvq Zua'q ninb Bua yaag maiq tuvq Zauj ninb Bua Bx'q Jaaj weig zu'g yia maiq zx'q yetg teij am-mon myenb Eei Dau pun meib Bua. naaiq nxm teib puv yia Jiu pun lotq Eei zeib fun penj ninb Bua Eei pwrng mig a'q.”
2.31: uaq zang zyruq Buaj yia, “mavg maa'b! yia zx'q si-honj huvb Zauj ninb Eei teib puv Jiu pun meib Bua. xij zu'g pia'g mivb kunq cvj yem Fiag penj meib Bua Ripg Eei pwrng.”
2.30: mq paag hetq-Bon zivb Eei si-honj huvb maiq Kavq pun Bua yavb ninb Eei teib puv Jiaj, weig zu'g zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, zruj pun si-honj huvb Eei Hruq vcvg, maiq Kavq mwavj, weig zx'q ninb Jiu pun yem meib Bua Eei puab Diaq Navq ib Jaaj Nxi nx.
2.27: “Toq pun yia Bua Jiaj meib Eei teib puv. yia Bua Kuvj yavb tomb Jauq Jiaj Navq, maiq mivb zaaij, maiq mivb Byaaug.
2.11: naaiq teij e-mim myenb yaag Navq aa-naakq myenb nx. myenb funj ninb Bua zruj le-faa-im myenb, mq paag mo-apg myenb heug ninb Bua zruj e-mim myenb.
2.5: maiq tuvq Zauj ninb Bua Bx'q Jaaj. ninb Bua Eei Dau, lyemb yetg nxm zaub penq Zaaiq Eei txvj, yia yaag maiq pun meib Bua, weig zu'g yia zx'q sej-i Bov Jiu pun e-saau mig a'q.
2.9: zyruq cvj Buaj yia, “maiq tuvq Zua'q mo-apg myenb yaag maiq tuvq Zauj ninb Bua Bx'q Jaaj weig zu'g yia maiq pun yetg teij ninb Bua Eei Dau meib Bua. yia zx'q aan zivb pun lotq Eei zeib fun, penj ninb Bua Eei pwrng mig a'q.”
2.16: Navq naaig, zuaq yem zwavj myenb ka'Euad haib zruj tu'q pcv naaiq teij myenb taig Revg,
2.37: mq paag ziuj zyruq, Bua Eei Tinb huvb, hatg Eei waag, Bua maiq mivb fatq am-mon myenb Eei kapg Jaaij Eei haiq nxm txvj, se maiq kan yapq-Bxkg Daaib Len Eei yetg zuvq Dau Zauj Bov zavg txvj Eei zivb.
2.4: xij zu'g Buaj pc'g fivj, ‘meib Bua Eei kxb yrud, e-saau Eei zeib fun, yem sej-i teig. meib Bua yaag xij zu'g yavb ninb Bua Eei kapg Jaaij Jiaj. ninb Bua xij kamb Riaj meib Bua, mq paag meib Bua zuvq xij zu'g faij fim.
2.10: (zinb Daavg maaib e-mim myenb yem uaq nxm txvj, se yetg fivj Zamq Eei myenb, yrug Lo yrug Lav Navq aa-naakq myenb.
2.22: zyruq yaag fib Navq Eei yem e-saau Eei zeib fun Eei uaq Daavg mcvj myetg ho-li myenb. e-saau Eei zeib fun zyrug Rcv tu'q uaq nxm teib puv yem Fiag Tauj ib Jaaj Nxi.
2.12: zinb Daavg ho-li myenb yem sej-i teig mq paag e-saau Eei zeib fun zung ninb Bua Zwrtq, myetg Jyenq ninb Bua mivb zyrug yem Jyenq ninb Bua Eei teib puv Navq i-saa-laa-en myenb yem zyruq Jiu pun ninb Bua Eei teib puv uaq nx.)
2.15: se zyruq kanb zruj pun naaiq teij yem Zyavq Eei myenb Tauj ninb Bua zu'g myetg Revg.
2.13: zyruq kxvq, “xij zu'g Zwrtq Jauq Jiaj ze-letq hxvd.” yia Bua zyrug Jiaj ze-letq hxvd mig a'q.
2.1: yem kau, Bua zyrug taauj sin Rwrnj teib puvb Waav, yavb mivb Kxib si'q uaq tiub Jauq Navq zyruq Buaj yia zruj nx. Bua lovg zyavb hog Daauq Eei yrub Jyenq kan sej-i Bov mivb.
2.26: yem Ke-De-motq teib puvb Waav yia Paaiq myenb mivb hetq-Bon zivb Eei si-honj huvb, Zauj ninb kxvq pcvb xn Eei waag,
2.25: yem ib Nxi mivb yia xij pun luvb Diaq maang fivj kamb Riaj haig meib Bua, zuvq haid Hruq waaig Revg. myenb yetq haid kxvq Tauj meib Bua Eei Jaub lrug nx, ninb Bua kamb Riaj, sin zinj, Raub tu'q Kruq haig.”

20.18: maiq zei c'q, ninb Bua Faauj meib Bua kan Jyenq ninb Bua zavg ninb Bua Eei zyenb, zruj uaq teij yruj haig, kamb Riaq haig Eei sig. meib Bua zyrug paamd zwid txvg zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb.
20.3: “o i-saa-laa-en myenb aag, mwavj lovj og. ib Nxi meib Bua xij zu'g Zwrtq mivb Zauj meib Bua Eei winb wavq Bx'q Jaaj. maiq tuvq Hruq mau, maiq tuvq kamb Riaj, maiq tuvq Hruq lung fai zu'g winb wavq hc'q meib Bua,
20.8: pcvb pyeiq xij zu'g cvj Buaj ninb Bua Eei zwavj pcv, “haiq taub kamb Riaj, Hruq mau? maaib nx, kunq Rwrnj pyauq a'q. Riaj haib zruj pun ninb Eei Jwavg zruj pcv Eei txig Hruq mau Navq ninb nx.”
20.19: meib Bua xij Bx'q haiq nxm zivb zyrug weib Jyenq laub Eei, maiq tuvq lovg pruq Va'q waaig Dyavj, weig zu'g meib Bua haib Eang naaiq teij Dyavj Eei pyruq. maiq tuvq kxij. Deig Eei Dyavj maiq zeid meib Bua Eei winb wavq.
20.9: pcvb pyeiq Zauj pcv kxvq liud, ninb Bua xij zu'g Paaiq teij myenb zruj pyeiq kunq yetg kwanb yetg kwanb pcv.
20.7: maaib haiq taub kxvq zyavb auq yaag maiq kcvb zruj Zivb Jaa? maaib nx, kunq Rwrnj pyauq a'q. Riaj Bx'q Jaaj zu'g taig, kanb taub zyrug lovg ninb Eei auq.”
20.5: pcvb pyeiq xij zu'g kxvq Buaj ninb Bua Eei pcv, “maaib haiq taub komq zyavj syavb pyauq yaag maiq kcvb fuvj pun Tinb huvb? maaib nx, kunq Rwrnj pyauq a'q. Riaj Bx'q Jaaj zu'g taig, kanb taub zyrug fuvj ninb Eei pyauq.
20.16: mq paag zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, pun meib Bua Ripg uaq teij fivb fivj myenb Eei zivb, ta'faanb haib Tauq Qiaj Eei ka'naaiq xij zu'g taij Revg, maiq tuvq lyrub yetg taub.
20.20: ta'faanb hiuq tu'q maiq zeid zyavb pyruq Eei Dyavj kxij tu'q Eei, weig lovg zruj Jaab sig Bx'q meib Bua weib kxmj uaq nxm zivb Tauj zivb Baav.
20.17: xij zu'g myetg Revg naaiq teij myenb, se hitq-Tai myenb, aa-mo-lai myenb, Kaa-naa-an myenb, pe-litq-si myenb, hi-wai myenb Zauj ye-Butg myenb, ziuj zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, hatg Eei waag.
20.14: mq paag msia'q txn Zauj fu'Jweiq, scvb Kuq Zauj yem zivb ka'Euad Eei yetg zuvq ka'naaiq haib lovg penj meib Bua kanb luq taaib Eei ka'naaiq. meib Bua luq winb wavq Eei yetg zuvq ka'naaiq meib Bua lovg tu'q Eei. zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, zx'q naaiq teij ka'naaiq Jiu pun meib Bua lovg.
20.4: weig zu'g zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Zauj meib Bua mivb, xij weig meib Bua Bx'q meib Bua Eei winb wavq, pun meib Bua tu'q hivb.”
20.2: aaq lamb Zwrtq mivb Bx'q Jaaj uaq zang, sai myenb zyrug yem pcv Eei Ra'Myen txij ninb Bua kxvq,
20.6: maaib haiq taub zwavj a'vung pyruq yaag maiq kcvb tu'q Eang? maaib nx, kunq Rwrnj pyauq a'q. Riaj Bx'q Jaaj zu'g taig, kanb taub zyrug tu'q Eang.
20.13: zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, zx'q uaq nxm zivb Jiu pun yem meib Bua Eei puab Diaq uaq zang, xij zu'g lovg Ru'g Daauq taij Revg naaiq nxm zivb Eei mJavg txn.
20.12: mq paag sij kxvq uaq nxm zivb Eei myenb maiq Eyemg mau, vcvg Jyenq meib Bua zyrug Zauj meib Bua Bx'q Jaaj, meib Bua xij zu'g weib Jyenq Bx'q uaq nxm zivb.
20.15: xij zu'g Navq naaiq zruj pun leib meib Bua ko uaq teij nxmb nxm zivb, ta'faanb maiq zeid nitq fatq naaiq teij fivb fivj myenb Eei zivb.
20.11: sij kxvq ninb Bua Eyemg mau, ninb Bua yaag Kxi zivb kcvb, yem uaq nxm zivb Eei zwavj myenb xij zu'g Tevj meib Bua zruj nrub, Bua'g meib Bua kunq.
20.1: meib Bua Zwrtq mivb Zauj winb wavq Bx'q Jaaj uaq zang, pwatg maad Zauj Bx'q Jaaj Eei maab Zia Zauj ninb Bua Eei pcv kaub Zamq meib Bua Eei, yaag maiq tuvq kamb Riaj weig zu'g zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, tovb txb meib Bua Zwrtq i-yipq teib puv uaq taub, Zauj meib Bua yem.
20.10: meib Bua mivb Tauj fatq teij tovb meib Bua xij Bx'q uaq nxm zivb, xij zu'g pun ninb Bua maaib Qavj Eyemg mau.

24.18: Javj Jyenq meib Bua yem i-yipq teib puv zruj Jiaj nrub, zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, yaag zua'g meib Bua Zwrtq. weig naaiq yia hatg meib Bua Navq naaiq nx zruj.

24.3: ta'Eeig taub Goj yaag maiq Namq ninb cvj fiaq leib Zai sru pun ninb zyrug heug ninb mivb mig a'q, fai ta'Eeig taub Goj taig mig a'q,
24.21: yem a'vung Wivj kc'q liud a'vung pyruq, zevg Fiag uaq teij maiq tuvq cvj mivb kc'q. xij zu'g lyrub Jyenq pun kanb fivj myenb Zauj kub hanb fu'Jweiq Zauj aub kwaaq.
24.14: maiq tuvq Kwei Zivq taaib Eei myenb Jomg myenb Zauj tavb tonj Eei myenb, maiq kunq Jwavg i-saa-laa-en fivj Eei kxb yrud fai yem meib Bua Eei zivb Eei kanb fivj myenb.
24.6: maiq tuvq zx'q myenb Eei mxg fai kub vwaaig uaq mcvj mxg zruj txvb taaub weig zu'g naaiq Euvg txvb taaub se myenb yuvd mcvg Eei ka'naaiq.
24.2: sij kxvq auq Zwrtq pyauq mivb cvj lovg kanb taub Goj,
24.20: meib Bua Pyu'q ka'lanq pyruq, zevg Fiag yem Gwaab Eei maiq tuvq cvj mivb Pyu'q. xij zu'g lyrub pun kanb fivj myenb Zauj kub hanb fu'Jweiq Zauj aub kwaaq.
24.7: sij kxvq zx'q tu'q myenb nimg Zauj ninb Jwavg fivj Eei i-saa-laa-en myenb lovg zruj nrub fai maaig ninb, uaq taub nimg myenb Eei myenb xij zu'g tivg zwid taij taig. Navq naaiq zruj zyrug pun yem meib Bua Bu'Dovj maiq maaib naaiq Euvg x'q sig.
24.19: meib Bua yem Deig kaatq Byaub yaag la'Ku'q Byaub zeiq uaq Deig, maiq tuvq taauj sin mivb zx'q. Zinb ninb yem uaq Deig penj kanb fivj myenb Zauj kub hanb fu'Jweiq Zauj aub kwaaq Eei pwrng. Navq naaig zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, xij Zeij fu'q meib Bua Eei puad zruj Eei yetg zuvq kov.
24.17: maiq tuvq Kwei kanb fivj myenb fai kub hanb fu'Jweiq pun ninb Bua maiq tu'q pcvb fim Eei pwrng. yaag maiq tuvq zx'q aub kwaaq Eei tomb lwi zruj txvb taaub.
24.11: xij zu'g yem ka'Eiag mcvj zuaq kaaq meib Bua Eei ka'naaiq uaq taub myenb kanb txb zruj txvb taaub Eei ka'naaiq Zwrtq taaib pun meib Bua.
24.5: lovg Jyenq syavb auq Eei myenb maiq tuvq Paaiq ninb mivb zruj pcv, yaag maiq tuvq heug ninb Daam haiq Euvg tomb zwavj Eei kov. xij zu'g pun ninb tu'q yem pyauq yetg Havj weig pun ninb Eei auq Fyenb yrub.
24.9: xij zu'g Javj Jyenq, Zwrtq i-yipq teib puv kan Jauq taaib uaq zang, zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Navq haiq nx zruj pun mi-lyem.
24.16: maiq tuvq weig txnb Jweiq zruj Eei zwid taij tiaj maag. yaag maiq tuvq weig tiaj maag zruj Eei zwid taij txnb Jweiq. kx'g myenb xij zu'g weig kx'g myenb Eei zwid zu'g taig.
24.4: taaub taub Goj, tovb zung ninb pyauj uaq taub, cvj lovg ninb zruj auq maiq tu'q a'q, weig zu'g uaq taub auq maaib wij. ziuj zyruq mavg, naaiq se kamb Riaq haig, yruj haig Eei sig. maiq tuvq pun zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Jiu pun meib Bua Ripg Eei teib puv zu'g maaib zwid.
24.10: meib Bua kaaq ka'naaiq pun myenb, maiq tuvq pia'g ninb Eei pyauq zx'q ninb xij lovg zruj txvb taaub Eei ka'naaiq.
24.22: xij zu'g Javj Jyenq zinb Daavg meib Bua yem i-yipq teib puv zruj Jiaj nrub. weig naaiq yia Zivj hatg meib Bua Navq naaiq nx zruj.
24.12: sij kxvq uaq taub myenb Jomg haig, maiq tuvq syru ninb lovg zruj txvb taaub Eei ka'naaiq Jiaj mwrnd.
24.15: ta'faanb zruj kov Eei Nxi, Ba'Nxi maiq kcvb mwrtq Eei zyavb hog, xij zu'g pun ninb Eei kovb zinb, weig zu'g ninb Jomg haig, Kauj kovb zinb yuvd mcvg. sij kxvq maiq pun nx, ninb xij koj zyruq. meib Bua zyrug maaib zwid a'q.
24.13: Ba'Nxi mwrtq Eei zyavb hog zuvq xij zu'g fuvj lovg zruj txvb taaub Eei tomb lwi Rwrnj weig pun ninb homg Jyenq pweij yaag pwav waag pun meib Bua. ziuj zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb mavg, meib Bua zruj tu'q hxpg.
24.1: sij kxvq myenb lovg Jyenq auq, Ga'haaq haid maiq hxpg Hruq ninb Eei auq weig zu'g pwatg ninb Eei auq zruj sig maiq zyavb hxvb, Goj zyrug fiaq leib Zai sru pun Jyenq ninb yaag heug ninb Zwrtq pyauq mivb a'q.

28.18: meib Bua xij zu'g zyruj, zyrug pun meib Bua maiq maaib fu'Jweiq Zamq, pun Dau Eei kcvb zwavj maiq penj, pun meib Bua Eei vovb txn Zauj pa'ki yuvb txn yaag zo'g.
28.45: meib Bua zyrug zu'g syrug naaiq teij yetg zuvq zyruj Eei waag Tauj meib Bua zu'g myetg, weig zu'g meib Bua maiq mwavj zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Eei waag, maiq ei ninb Jiu pun meib Bua Eei livg Zauj leid.
28.3: yem zivb ka'Euad meib Bua xij tu'q fu'q, yem livb teig yaag tu'q fu'q.
28.66: meib Bua zanb zang Raub Jyenq meib Bua Eei mcvg, zyavb Nxi zyavb mwrnd kamb Riaj Jyenq, maiq hiuq haiq Nxi navb haiq Nxi taig.
28.43: yem meib Bua Bu'Dovj Eei kanb fivj myenb xij kunq zruj kunq faauj Lav. meib Bua kanb kunq zruj kunq Dxtq Fiag aiq.
28.50: naaiq fivj myenb Eei Myenb mweig Zyruq, ninb Bua maiq Taaib myenb koj myenb yaag maiq Kxb lyenb myenb lunj myenb.
28.14: maiq tuvq vcvg yia ib Nxi hatg meib Bua Eei haiq Jruj waag, maiq tuvq pua'g zavg kanb taub zyenb.
28.48: weig naaiq, meib Bua xij zu'g Hruq sia Jaav Gaatq, lcvb kcvq Eei yem, Jomg Tauj Do'q, maiq maaib haiq Euvg, Zxg zu'g fub suj zyruq Paaiq taaib Bx'q meib Bua Eei winb wavq. zyruq xij hxig meib Bua Kruq Tauj meib Bua zu'g myetg Revg.
28.34: meib Bua Eei mziv pwatg Eei Euvb Euvg sig zyrug zruj pun meib Bua maiq Rav.
28.2: sij kxvq meib Bua mwavj zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Eei waag, meib Bua zyrug tu'q Revg naaiq teij fu'q.
28.36: zyruq xij txb meib Bua Zauj meib Bua lyepg taaib kunq meib Bua Eei huvb mivb Tauj tovb meib Bua Zauj meib Bua Eei ovb Taaij maiq hiuq Eei kua'q. yem uaq meib Bua zyrug zavg kanb taub zyenb, se lovg Dyavj, lovg la'pyeiq zruj taaib Eei zyenb.
28.35: zyruq xij pun meib Bua Eei Zivb Bx'g zyavb to'g haig, zxg maiq lovj Eei zweib, yaag yem zaub Diaq zyavb Tauj mGxvb pcvb.

29.18: xij zu'g faij fim, Riaj yem meib Bua Bu'Dovj Eei haiq taub mJavg msia'q fai haiq pwrng, haiq fivj myenb kwavg zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, mivb zavg uaq teij kua'q Eei zyenb. Riaj yem meib Bua Bu'Dovj haib Navq maaib kxn Zwrtq im haig, haib lcvg myenb Eei pyruq.
29.8: Bua Zaavq Revg ninb Bua Eei teib puv Jiu pun lu-Ben fivj, kaatg fivj, Zauj maa-natq-sej Eei Daamb fivj.
29.3: meib Bua kanb Eei mziv tu'q pwatg uaq teij tomb ze'g naang Zauj Bua'g hxvb Eei sig Zauj Javb hog.
29.21: zyruq xij yem fivb fivj i-saa-laa-en myenb Bu'Dovj zx'q ninb Du'g laanb myenb Zwrtq, pun ninb zu'g Kruq, ziuj naaiq pwrnq leib latg sru fiaq Jyenq Eei vcvg waag zu'g zyruj.
29.14: yia maiq taan Zauj meib Bua lyepg naaiq teij vcvg waag,
29.23: naaiq nxm teib puv Kuvj maaib huvb, maaib Rauq, penj Daub Waav, weig zu'g trud puaq Qwi mig a'q. maiq maaib haiq taub zwavj ka'naaiq yaag maiq maaib haiq Euvg kcvb zwavj Zwrtq. lyemb miaq yaag maiq Zwrtq. zyruq xij pun teib puv zu'g paaig Navq ninb Qiaj Jiad! haig zyrug zruj pun soj-Dom, ko-mo-laa, atg-maa Zauj sej-Bo-yim zu'g paaig uaq nx.
29.6: meib Bua maiq tu'q Eang Fuaq yaag maiq tu'q hopq a'vung tiuq fai tiub Kuq. yia Navq naaiq zruj weig pun meib Bua hiuq tu'q yia se zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb.
29.2: mo-se heug i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb kapq zunq zyrug kxvq Buaj ninb Bua, meib Bua kanb Eei mziv tu'q pwatg yem i-yipq teib puv, zyruq Navq haiq nx zruj pun faa-lo huvb Zauj ninb Eei zwavj Jyen Zauj kxmj ninb Eei teib puv.
29.20: zyruq yetg liud maiq kwavg naaiq Euvg myenb Eei zwid. zyruq Qiaj Jiad, hang kau, zyrug pun naaiq laanb myenb syrug fiaq Jyenq naaiq pwrnq sru yetg zuvq zyruj Eei waag Tauj zu'g myetg Revg, maiq tu'q yem naaiq luvb Diaq.
29.24: maang fivj myenb zuvq xij naaig, “zyruq weig haiq tiug Navq naaiq nx zruj pun naaiq nxm teib puv? ninb weig haiq tiug Dovg naaig Qiaj Jiad?”
29.28: zyruq nrud haig, Qiaj Jiad Jyenq pcv ninb Bua Zwrtq taaib kwavg yem kanb nxm kua'q Navq ib Jaaj Nxi nx.”
29.7: meib Bua taaib Tauj naaiq nxm teib puv uaq zang hetq-Bon zivb Eei si-honj huvb Zauj Baa-saan Eei okg huvb, Zwrtq taaib Zauj Bua Bx'q Jaaj mq paag Bua Bx'q hivb ninb Bua.
29.29: kem Jyenq Eei sig se zyruq, Bua Eei Tinb huvb Eei. laaug yaavb Eei sig yetg liud penj Bua Eei Zauj Bua Eei zeib fun Eei, weig pun Bua haib ei Jyenq naaiq teij leib latg Eei yetg zuvq waag zruj.
29.19: sij kxvq maaib taub naaiq Euvg myenb haid naaiq teij hruq Eei vcvg waag, ninb yem Hruq haid Navq pwav waag ninb kanb zyrug laaig, “maiq kunq sweib eij zruj, yia Zxg haib tu'q lovj Eei.” Navq naaig, maiq kunq Kuq myenb fai x'q myenb, yetg zuvq xij zu'g myetg Revg.
29.17: meib Bua tu'q pwatg yem ninb Bua Bu'Dovj lovg Dyavj, lovg la'pyeiq fai Jyem Eaanb zruj taaib uaq teij yruj haig, kamb Riaq haig Eei miub favj.
29.27: weig naaiq zyruq Qiaj Jiad! haig naaiq nxm teib puv, pun ninb Bua zu'g zyruj Navq naaiq pwrnq sru fiaq Jyenq Eei waag.
29.11: meib Bua Eei aub Jweiq, yem meib Bua Eei Dopg liub Zyavq Eei kanb fivj myenb, Zauj Tevj meib Bua kc'q zaavb Daam uam Eei myenb, taaib kapq zunq sruq Jyenq zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Eei Ra'Myen.
29.5: yia txb meib Bua yem teib puvb Waav uaq teij feij zyepg Havj ka'Euad, meib Bua zu'q Eei lwib hruj yaag maiq huq. meib Bua taapg Eei heb yaag maiq waaig.
29.9: meib Bua xij zu'g zyepg zua'q Eei kan lovj naaiq teij vcvg waag weig pun meib Bua zruj Eei Euvb Euvg tu'q lovj.
29.16: meib Bua hiuq tu'q Bua yem i-yipq teib puv uaq zang Bua Navq haiq nx yem, yaag hiuq tu'q Bua Jiaj uaq teij Zamb fivj myenb Eei kua'q Navq haiq nx Jiaj.
29.4: mq paag Tauj ib Nxi zyruq maiq pun meib Bua Eei Hruq haib mevb pc'g, maiq pun meib Bua Eei mziv haib mavg tu'q pwatg, yaag maiq pun meib Bua Eei mnxmb haib mwavj tu'q haid.
29.10: ib Nxi meib Bua fivb fivj Eei pyeiq zeiq Zauj myenb koj, meib Bua Eei Jyen, i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei yetg zwavj mJavg txn,
29.22: meib Bua txig Jiaj txig Ga'haaq hivq Zwrtq seij Eei zeib fun Zauj yem ko Eei teib puv taaib Eei kanb fivj myenb zyrug pwatg naaiq nxm teib puv zu'g pwavb Eei tomb sig Zauj zyruq pun teib puv zu'g Eei Euvb Euvg pcvg.
29.12: meib Bua taaib weig zipq zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, hruq Jyenq Zauj meib Bua lcvd Jiad Eei vcvg waag, se tovb ib Nxi zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Zauj meib Bua lyepg Jiad Eei vcvg waag.
29.15: se maiq zeid Kuvj Zauj yia Bua sruq Jyenq naaiq yem zyruq, Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Eei Ra'Myen uaq teij Navq. yia yaag Zauj Ga'haaq hivq maiq kcvb Zwrtq seij Eei zeib fun lyepg naaiq teij vcvg waag.
29.13: ib Nxi zyruq xij lyepg meib Bua penj ninb kanb Eei pc'g fivj. ninb zyrug penj meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Navq ninb Zauj meib Bua lcvd, yaag Navq ninb Zauj meib Bua Eei ovb Taaij, apg-laa-ham, i-sakg, Zauj yaa-Kopq hruq Jyenq lcvd uaq nx.
29.1: naaiq teij waag se yem mo-apg uaq zang, zyruq hatg mo-se Zauj i-saa-laa-en myenb lyepg Eei vcvg waag, Tipq Jyenq yem ho-lepq ninb Zauj ninb Bua lyepg Eei vcvg waag.
29.26: ninb Bua mivb fub suj paaij tovb ninb Bua maiq paaij Jiaj Eei zyenb, se zyruq maiq pun ninb Bua zavg Eei zyenb.
29.25: myenb zyrug tau, “se weig zu'g naaiq teij myenb kwavg zyruq, ninb Bua Eei ovb Taaij Eei Tinb huvb, txb ninb Bua Zwrtq i-yipq teib puv Eei zyavb hog Zauj ninb Bua lyepg Eei vcvg waag.

19.18: syemq zwid Jyen zyrug lovb lovj Eei zaab mwrng ninb Bua Eei sig. sij kxvq zaab Zwrtq zxvb zevj myenb kxvb pc'g, zruj Jaaq zxvb zevj hxig ninb Eei kxb yrud,
19.3: xij zu'g Kxi Jauq mivb Tauj uaq teij zivb, yaag zx'q zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Jiu pun meib Bua Ripg Eei teib puv pun zruj pua kruq weig pun Za'g prug taij myenb Eei myenb haib pyauj mivb uaq teij zivb yem.
19.8: sij kxvq zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Zapq meib Bua Eei kapg Jaaij Zwrtq ziuj ninb hruq pun meib Bua Eei ovb Taaij, yaag zx'q ninb lcvd pun ninb Bua Eei teib puv yetg zuvq Jiu pun meib Bua,
19.19: xij zu'g zruj pun ninb Navq ninb Jiad Hruq zruj pun ninb Eei kxb yrud nx. xij zu'g pun naaiq teij x'q sig yem meib Bua Bu'Dovj zutg Revg.
19.9: yaag ta'faanb meib Bua ei Jyenq yia ib Nxi hatg meib Bua Eei yetg zuvq leid, se Namq zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, zanb zang yavb ninb Eei Jauq, meib Bua xij zu'g cvj kanb Za'levg Tipq pua nxm zivb.
19.7: weig naaiq yia hatg meib Bua xij zu'g kanb Za'levg kinq Zwrtq pua nxm zivb.
19.5: Navq myenb Zauj taub Jwavg laavd Eei txig pia'g lomg kxij Dyavj. ninb fevj pruq kxij Dyavj uaq zang, pruq Dutq mivb Bx'q zu'g ninb Eei txig taig. ninb zyrug pyauj mivb yetg nxm naaiq teij zivb Fruj ninb Eei mcvg.
19.16: sij kxvq maaib taub myenb zruj Jaaq zxvb zevj xij hxig myenb,
19.20: zwavj myenb haid naaiq teij sig zyrug kamb Riaj haig. yem meib Bua Bu'Dovj yetg liud maiq maaib myenb kaamq zruj naaiq Euvg x'q sig.
19.17: naaiq teij i taub maaib sig Eei myenb xij zu'g mivb yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen, txv Jyenq tovb uaq zang zruj sai myenb Eei kov Eei sai myenb Zauj syemq zwid Jyen.
19.14: meib Bua yem zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb Jiu pun meib Bua Eei teib puv, maiq tuvq swiq Jwavg laavd myenb Eei Daub teig kapg Genj zruj Javb hog Eei la'pyeib tovg. naaiq se zinb paan myenb tivg taaib Eei kapg Jaaij.
19.4: yem naaiq mivb kxvq myenb taij myenb pyauj mivb yem siaj mcvg zivb weig Fruj mcvg Eei Jaub lrug, se myenb Za'g prug taij zu'g myenb taig, maiq zeid laanb hang laanb taij.
19.21: maiq tuvq Kxb lyenb naaiq Euvg myenb. xij zu'g mcvg Jaauq mcvg, mziv Jaauq mziv, Eaab Jaauq Eaab, puad Jaauq puad, zauj Jaauq zauj.
19.2: xij zu'g yem zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Jiu pun meib Bua Ripg uaq nxm teib puv kanb Za'levg kinq Zwrtq pua nxm zivb.
19.6: maiq zei c'q, xij Jaauq myenb mcvg win uaq taub Qiaj Jiad! haig, zung ninb. sij kxvq Jauq pa'la'g ko, zung tu'q zaaig yaag taij ninb maiq kunq maiq hxpg zu'g taig, weig zu'g ninb maiq zeid hang ninb Eei txig Zivj taij.
19.13: meib Bua maiq tuvq Kxb lyenb ninb. yem i-saa-laa-en myenb Bu'Dovj xij zu'g pun maiq maaib taij maiq zruj txvg Eei myenb Eei sig, weig pun meib Bua tu'q lovj.
19.12: ninb kanb Eei pwrnb zivb Eei myenb koj xij zu'g Paaiq myenb mivb zx'q ninb Rwrnj taaib Jiu pun Jaauq myenb mcvg win uaq taub taij ninb taig.
19.15: maiq kunq myenb paamd haiq Euvg zwid fai zruj txvg haiq Euvg sig, Du'g taub myenb zruj zxvb zevj se maiq kauj tivg ninb Eei zwid. xij zu'g maaib i fai pua taub zruj zxvb zevj Zivj tivg.
19.11: mq paag sij kxvq maaib taub myenb Rxv Zauj ninb Jwavg laavd myenb zyrug pivj Jyenq zuaq Bx'q taig ninb, uaq taub zyrug pyauj mivb Tauj yetg nxm uaq teij siaj mcvg zivb,
19.1: zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, zx'q ninb xij Jiu pun meib Bua uaq nxm teib puv uaq teij kua'q Eei myenb Pai kwavg uaq zang, meib Bua yaag tu'q zung ninb Bua Zwrtq, pia'g mivb yem Jyenq ninb Bua Eei zivb Zauj ninb Bua Eei pyauq,
19.10: xij zu'g Tipq naaiq teij zivb weig pun maiq zruj txvg Eei myenb yem zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Jiu pun meib Bua Ripg Eei teib puv maiq zu'g taij taig. meib Bua kanb yaag maiq zu'g weig naaiq teij sig zu'g Daamb txv.

17.18: ninb faauj ninb Eei kua'q Eei weig zruj huvb Eei zyavb hog, xij zu'g weig kanb Zeu le-wi sai myenb kruj Jyenq uaq Fung leib latg sru.
17.3: vcvg yia hatg Eei waag, mivb zavg Eiag Eei zyenb zyrug paaij uaq teij zyenb, fai paaij Ba'Nxi fai Laaj fai kub vwaaig luvb Eei ka'naaiq,
17.8: sij kxvq yem meib Bua Eei muvq maaib a'g tu'q tunj Eei sig, se myenb taij myenb ninb Bua Za'g prug taij fai paab paag taij, Rcv Jaab tivb ka'naaiq, fai zruj pun myenb zu'g mun Eei sig, xij zu'g txb mivb zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, xij kinq taaib Eei txvj.
17.19: Zeu taaib an ninb uaq pun ninb yetg seij zanb zang to'g, ho'g ling Taaib zyruq, ninb Eei Tinb huvb. ninb xij zu'g lovb lovj Eei kan naaiq teij leib latg Eei Jrub Jruj waag Zauj tiub tiub leid,
17.9: mivb lxd le-wi sai myenb Zauj txij uaq zang zruj syemq zwid Jyen uaq taub, Toq ninb Bua Tevj. ninb Bua zyrug Tevj meib Bua tunj sig.
17.7: zruj zxvb zevj Eei myenb xij zu'g Fiag puad zov ninb Daavg. Ga'haaq zwavj myenb Tevj Jyenq zov. Navq naaig zyrug pun yem meib Bua Bu'Dovj Eei x'q sig zutg Revg.
17.5: xij zu'g zx'q zruj naaiq Euvg x'q sig Eei myenb, maiq kunq mJavg fai msia'q, txb ninb mivb Tauj zivb laatg kcvb ka'Eiag mcvj lovg la'pyeiq zov taig.
17.16: zruj huvb Eei myenb maiq tuvq weig kanb maaib maad Zamq, yaag maiq tuvq pun pc'g fivj cvj Rwrnj i-yipq teib puv weig Tipq maad Zamq Jyenq faauj, weig zu'g zyruq Buaj Jiaj meib Bua, “maiq tuvq cvj Rwrnj i-yipq teib puv.”
17.20: weig pun kanb maiq Zevb Lo funj kanb kaub lovj kxb yrud zyrug vcvg naaiq teij haiq tiub leid. Navq naaig ninb Zauj ninb Eei zeib fun tu'q kunq i-saa-laa-en kua'q laub Eei.
17.17: zruj huvb Eei myenb yaag maiq tuvq maaib auq Zamq. Riaj haib zruj pun ninb leib Tinb huvb. yaag maiq tuvq weig ninb kanb syru Jyem Eaanb Zamq.
17.14: meib Bua tu'q pia'g mivb yem Jyenq zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Jiu pun meib Bua Ripg Eei teib puv uaq zang, meib Bua zyrug kxvq, “Bua xij zu'g lyepg taub huvb kunq Bua Navq weib kxmj Bua uaq teij kua'q Eei myenb nx.”
17.4: naaiq teij sig yaag maaib myenb Buaj meib Bua, meib Bua yaag haid mig a'q, xij zu'g lovb lovj Eei zaab mavg. sij kxvq hiuq tu'q naaiq teij sig za'kevb maaib nx, yaag hiuq tivg yem i-saa-laa-en myenb Bu'Dovj maaib myenb zruj naaiq teij yruj haig, kamb Riaq haig Eei sig,
17.2: yem zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Zeij pun meib Bua Eei haiq nxm muvq, sij kxvq maaib haiq taub mJavg fai msia'q ei zyruq mavg, pwatg ninb zruj waaig sig txvg ninb lcvd Eei vcvg waag,
17.6: xij zu'g maaib i pua taub zxvb zevj myenb zruj zxvb zevj Zivj tivg ninb Eei zwid zu'g taig. Kuvj maaib Du'g taub zruj zxvb zevj Navq, maiq tuvq taij haiq taub.
17.13: zwavj myenb haid naaiq teij sig zyrug kamb Riaj, Ga'haaq maiq maaib haiq taub kaamq vcvg.
17.12: sij kxvq haiq taub vcvg Jyenq, maiq mwavj yem uaq fub suj zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Eei sai myenb fai syemq zwid Jyen, uaq taub zuvq xij zu'g taij taig. Navq naaig zyrug pun yem i-saa-laa-en myenb Bu'Dovj maiq maaib naaiq Euvg x'q sig.
17.15: meib Bua xij zu'g lyepg zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, kinq taaib Eei myenb Navq. xij zu'g lyepg taub meib Bua kanb Eei kxb yrud. maiq tuvq lyepg kanb fivj myenb, tovb maiq zeid i-saa-laa-en fivj Eei kxb yrud, zruj huvb kunq meib Bua.
17.11: xij zu'g ziuj ninb Bua Faauj meib Bua Eei leid Zauj ninb Bua tunj Eei waag. xij zu'g ei Revg, maiq tuvq vcvg haiq tiub.
17.1: maiq tuvq lovg waaig favj fai maaib txvj Gemb Eei vovb fai pa'ki yuvb fovg hxg ziag pun zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb. Navq naaiq se zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, yruj haig, kamb Riaq haig Eei sig.
17.10: yem zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, xij kinq taaib Eei txvj ninb Bua Navq haiq nx Buaj meib Bua, xij zu'g Navq uaq nx zruj. xij zu'g faij fim, ei Jyenq ninb Bua Paaiq zyavj Eei yetg zuvq waag zruj.

31.18: Tauj uaq Nxi yia zuvq xij pwav Jyenq yia Eei Myen, maiq mavg ninb Bua, laaij ninb Bua zruj yetg zuvq waaig sig, paaij Eiag Eei zyenb.
31.8: zyruq kanb xij yem meib Eei uaq Daavg mcvj. ninb yetg liud maiq puvj Dxtq meib yaag maiq kwavg meib. maiq tuvq kamb Riaj yaag maiq tuvq Hruq Waav.”
31.3: zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb kanb, xij mivb Daavg yend meib Bua, yem meib Bua Eei uaq Daavg mcvj myetg Revg uaq teij fivb fivj myenb. meib Bua zyrug tu'q ninb Bua Eei teib puv penj meib Bua Eei pwrng teib puv. yo-su-waa xij mivb Daavg txb meib Bua Navq zyruq kxvq uaq nx.
31.21: ninb Bua zu'g ziaj Euvg ze'g naang Zauj Zyruq Eei sig Eei zyavb hog, naaiq tiub Ruv zyrug zruj zxvb zevj koj ninb Bua, weig zu'g ninb Bua Eei zeib fun zanb zang pwib naaiq tiub Ruv, maiq la'Ku'q. maiq kunq yia maiq kcvb txb ninb Bua pia'g yia hruq pun ninb Bua Eei teib puv, ninb Bua Eei Hruq xij Navq haiq nx zruj yia zuvq hiuq mig a'q.”
31.14: zyruq kxvq Buaj mo-se, “meib kwei seij Eei Nxib Eia'g Tauj fatq a'q. xij zu'g heug yo-su-waa Zauj meib mivb wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub, yia zyrug Paaiq ninb.” mo-se Zauj yo-su-waa zyrug pia'g wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub ka'Euad.
31.23: zyruq Navq naaiq nx Paaiq nun Eei txn, yo-su-waa, “meib xij zu'g henq, taamq Lo Eei, weig zu'g meib zuvq xij zu'g txb i-saa-laa-en myenb pia'g yia hruq pun ninb Bua Eei teib puv. yia kanb xij Zauj meib yem.”
31.6: meib Bua xij zu'g henq, zuvj Jyenq taamq. maiq tuvq kamb Riaj ninb Bua zyrug hc'q kanb, weig zu'g zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Zauj meib Bua mivb. ninb yetg liud maiq puvj Dxtq meib Bua yaag maiq kwavg meib Bua.”
31.2: ninb kxvq, “yia ib zang pwavq yetg pc'q Eig zyepg Havj a'q. yia maiq haib txb maiq tu'q meib Bua. zyruq Buaj yia, ‘meib maiq tu'q Jiaj Jx-Dcn Daaib.’
31.20: yia xij txb ninb Bua pia'g uaq nxm Daub Truq lovj Eei teib puv, se tovb yia Zauj ninb Bua Eei ovb Taaij hruq Jyenq lcvd pun Eei teib puv. yem uaq nxm teib puv ninb Bua tu'q Eang peuq yaag Kub yem. ninb Bua zyrug Win mivb zavg Eiag Eei zyenb kwavg yia, yaag paamd yia Zauj ninb Bua lcvd Eei vcvg waag.
31.24: mo-se zx'q naaiq teij leib latg Eei waag yem kxn Tauj setq mweid fiaq Fiag sru Revg mig a'q.
31.28: xij zu'g heug meib Bua fivb fivj Eei zwavj myenb koj Zauj meib Bua Eei yetg zuvq Jyen taaib kapq zunq. yia zyrug kxvq naaiq teij waag pun ninb Bua mwavj yaag heug luvb Zauj Dau zruj zxvb zevj koj ninb Bua.
31.7: mo-se heug yo-su-waa taaib txv Jyenq i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb kxvq Buaj ninb, “meib xij zu'g henq, taamq Lo Eei, weig zu'g meib xij zu'g Zauj naaiq teij pc'g fivj pia'g zyruq Zauj ninb Bua Eei ovb Taaij lcvd Jiu pun ninb Bua Eei teib puv. meib xij zu'g txb ninb Bua pia'g mivb tu'q uaq nxm teib puv penj ninb Bua Eei pwrng.
31.29: weig zu'g yia hiuq tivg, yia taig mivb, Ga'haaq meib Bua xij kwavg yia hatg meib Bua Eei yetg zuvq waag, mivb zruj waaig sig. zyruq pwatg meib Bua zruj Eei x'q sig Zauj meib Bua Eei puad zruj Zwrtq Eei ka'naaiq, zyrug Zua'q ninb Qiaj Jiad haig Zivj taaib Ga'haaq hivq meib Bua xij zu'g tomb ze'g naang.”
31.19: “ib zang meib Bua xij zu'g fiaq naaiq tiub Ruv Faauj i-saa-laa-en myenb ho'g Tauj zua'g weig pun yia lovg zruj zxvb zevj koj ninb Bua.
31.17: Tauj uaq Nxi yia zyrug Qiaj Jiad haig ninb Bua yaag kwavg ninb Bua. yia xij pwav Jyenq yia Eei Myen, maiq mavg ninb Bua. ninb Bua zyrug zu'g myetg, zu'g Zyruq Eei sig Zauj tomb ze'g naang hxig ninb Bua. Tauj uaq Nxi ninb Bua zyrug naaig, ‘Bua zu'g naaiq teij ze'g naang laaij Bua Eei Tinb huvb maiq Zauj Bua yem maiq zeid?’
31.30: mo-se zyrug to'g txv naaiq tiub Ruv Eei waag pun i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb mwavj.
31.27: yia hiuq tu'q meib Bua Dovg haaij Hruq vcvg, mnxmb hod. yia Zxg zyavb Jyenq Zauj meib Bua yem Eei zyavb hog, meib Bua Dovg naaig vcvg zyruq, yia taig mivb Eei zyavb hog, meib Bua xij Dovg haaij vcvg maiq hiuq a'q.
31.11: i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb kapq zunq yem zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Eei Ra'Myen, se yem ninb kinq taaib Eei txvj uaq zang, meib xij zu'g to'g naaiq teij leib latg pun ninb Bua mwavj.
31.5: zyruq xij zx'q ninb Bua Jiu pun meib Bua. meib Bua xij zu'g ziuj yia hatg meib Bua Eei yetg zuvq waag zruj pun ninb Bua.
31.9: mo-se zyrug fiaq naaiq teij leib latg Jiu pun le-wi sai myenb, tovb kcv zyruq Eei lcvd vcvg waag faav Eei sai myenb, Zauj i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei zwavj myenb koj.
31.16: zyruq cvj kxvq Buaj mo-se, “maiq laub meib xij zu'g kwei seij. Ga'haaq naaiq teij pc'g fivj zyrug maiq zyepg zua'q Eei kan yia. ninb Bua xij mivb zavg tovb ninb Bua mivb yem uaq nxm teib puv Eei kanb fivj myenb Eei zyenb. ninb Bua xij kwavg yia yaag paamd yia Zauj ninb Bua lyepg Jiad Eei vcvg waag.
31.4: zyruq xij zruj pun uaq teij fivb fivj myenb Navq ninb zruj pun aa-mo-lai myenb Eei huvb, si-honj Zauj okg, lyemb ninb Bua Eei teib puv myetg Revg.
31.10: mo-se hatg ninb Bua, “mrud Rung pwavq siag Havj uaq Havj, se tovb kwavg zc'q Eei Havj, txij Byxq liub zipq Eei zyavb hog,
31.22: tovb uaq Nxi mo-se zyrug fiaq naaiq tiub Ruv taaib cvj Faauj i-saa-laa-en myenb.
31.12: xij zu'g heug zwavj myenb, lyemb mJavg msia'q Zauj fu'Jweiq, lyemb yem meib Bua Eei zivb Eei kanb fivj myenb, taaib kapq zunq weig pun ninb Bua tu'q haid yaag ho'g ling Taaib zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, yaag kan lovj naaiq teij leib latg Eei yetg zuvq waag.
31.15: zyruq hing taaib yem Bwrnb Dyrub ka'Euad, Dopg liub Eei kcvb Daavg kub vwaaig.
31.13: ninb Bua Eei zeib fun, tovb maiq haid Jiaj naaiq teij leib latg uaq teij, zyrug tu'q haid yaag ho'g ling Taaib zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, ta'faanb meib Bua tu'q yem Jyenq meib Bua ib zang xij Jiaj uaq vaang zi'g Jx-Dcn Daaib tu'q penj meib Bua Eei pwrng uaq nxm teib puv.”
31.1: mo-se cvj kxvq naaiq teij yetg zuvq waag Buaj i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb.
31.26: ninb kxvq, “zx'q naaiq Fung leib latg sru an Jyenq zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Eei lcvd vcvg waag faav ka'Len. an Jyenq naaig weig zruj zxvb zevj koj meib Bua i-saa-laa-en myenb.
31.25: ninb zyrug Paaiq kcv zyruq Eei lcvd vcvg waag faav Eei le-wi myenb.

30.18: ib Nxi yia mevb mevb Eei zunb Buaj meib Bua, meib Bua Dovg haaij zuvq xij zu'g myetg. meib Bua Jiaj Jx-Dcn Daaib pia'g xij penj meib Bua Eei pwrng uaq nxm teib puv meib Bua maiq tu'q zyavb laub.
30.3: zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, zyrug pun meib Bua tu'q lovj Navq lod uaq nx.  zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, xij Kxb lyenb meib Bua. ninb xij syru meib Bua, tovb ninb pun Raanj yem maang fivj Bu'Dovj Eei myenb, Rwrnj taaib kapq zunq.
30.8: meib Bua cvj xij Rwrnj taaib mwavj zyruq, yaag ei Revg yia ib Nxi Jiu pun meib Bua Eei yetg zuvq livg.
30.19: yia ib Nxi heug luvb Zauj Dau Tevj meib Bua zruj zxvb zevj, yia pun meib Bua maaib Qavj kinq xij zyavb fai taig, xij tu'q fu'q fai zu'g zyruj. ib zang xij zu'g kinq meib Bua xij tu'q zyavb Jyenq weig pun meib Bua Eei zeib fun haib tu'q zyavb Jyenq,
30.9: zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, xij pun meib Bua zruj Eei Euvb Euvg kov tu'q lovj, pun meib Bua tu'q fu'Jweiq Zamq, tu'q scvb Kuq Zamq, pun Dau Zwrtq kcvb zwavj lovj. zyruq cvj xij a'Neiq meib Bua, pun meib Bua tu'q lovj, Navq ninb a'Neiq meib Bua Eei ovb Taaij nx.
30.7: zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, xij pun meib Bua Eei winb wavq, tovb Rxv meib Bua, zruj to'g meib Bua uaq teij, zu'g naaiq teij yetg zuvq zyruj Eei waag.
30.5: zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, xij txb meib Bua pia'g mivb yem zinb Daavg penj meib Bua Eei ovb Taaij Eei teib puv, yaag xij pun meib Bua tu'q kaub lovj kaub penj, pun meib Bua kaub Yaavj meib Bua Eei ovb Taaij.
30.16: sij kxvq meib Bua ei Jyenq zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb Eei waag, tovb yia ib Nxi hatg meib Bua Eei waag, Namq zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, yavb ninb Eei tod, kan lovj ninb Eei leib latg Zauj livg Zauj leid, meib Bua zyrug tu'q zyavb Jyenq yaag Yaavj Jyenq faauj. meib Bua tu'q pia'g mivb yem Jyenq xij penj meib Bua Eei pwrng uaq nxm teib puv uaq zang, zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, xij Zeij fu'q pun meib Bua.
30.20: yaag Namq zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, mwavj ninb Eei waag, Kauj wrnq ninb. Navq naaig, meib Bua Zauj meib Bua Eei zeib fun tu'q zyavb syrug Ewrnb Daauq yem zyruq hruq Jyenq xij pun meib Bua Eei ovb Taaij, apg-laa-ham, i-sakg Zauj yaa-Kopq uaq nxm teib puv.
30.17: mq paag sij kxvq meib Bua Hruq vcvg, maiq Kavq mwavj zyruq, zyrug zu'g Duaq mivb fub suj zavg Eiag Eei zyenb,
30.14: uaq teij leib latg Zauj meib Bua yem naaiq, zuvq yem meib Bua Eei Rwib yaag yem meib Bua Eei Hruq weig pun meib Bua ei Jyenq zruj.
30.4: maiq kunq meib Bua zu'g Raanj mivb yem luvb Diaq kaub ko Jiaj Eei txvj, zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, xij yem uaq syru zunq, txb meib Bua Rwrnj taaib.
30.2: meib Bua Zauj meib Bua Eei zeib fun zyrug Rwrnj taaib lxd zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, yaag lovg Revg Hruq, lovg Revg za'eij, mwavj ib Nxi yia hatg meib Bua Eei yetg zuvq waag,
30.6: zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, xij Jamq meib Bua Zauj meib Bua Eei zeib fun Eei Hruq, pun meib Bua lovg Revg Hruq, lovg Revg za'eij Namq zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, weig pun meib Bua tu'q zyavb Jyenq.
30.13: naaiq teij leib latg yaag maiq zeid yem uaq vaang zi'g Kxiq zyrug xij zu'g naaig, “haiq taub xij Jiaj Kxiq mivb Tevj yia Bua zx'q taaib cvj zunb pun yia Bua mwavj yaag ei Jyenq zruj?”
30.12: se maiq zeid yem kub vwaaig luvb meib Bua zyrug kxvq, “haiq taub xij faauj luvb Tevj yia Bua zx'q Fiag cvj zunb pun yia Bua mwavj yaag ei Jyenq zruj?”
30.15: mavg maa'b! yia ib Nxi pun meib Bua maaib Qavj kinq xij maaib mcvg zyavb fai taig, tu'q lovj fai tu'q Zyruq.
30.11: yia ib Nxi hatg meib Bua Eei leib latg se maiq zeid weig meib Bua a'g Jiaj Daavg, yaag maiq zeid leib meib Bua ko.
30.1: yia txv Jyenq meib Bua kxvq naaiq teij waag, se yetg zuvq pwav Eei waag Zauj zyruj Eei waag, Zwrtq taaib txib tiug uaq zang, meib Bua yaag zu'g yem Raanj, yem zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, pun meib Bua yem uaq teij maang kua'q Bu'Dovj, meib Bua yaag Namb Rwrnj Javj zu'g naaiq teij waag,
30.10: ninb Navq naaiq zruj sij kxvq meib Bua mwavj zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb Eei waag, ei Jyenq naaiq pwrnq leib latg sru fiaq Jyenq Eei leib latg Zauj livg, yaag lovg Revg Hruq, lovg Revg za'eij Rwrnj taaib lxd zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb.

27.18: “+‘haiq taub txb mziv mcvb myenb yavb txvg Jauq, uaq taub zu'g zyruj a'q.’ “zwavj pc'g fivj zyrug kxvq, ‘aa-men.’

27.14: le-wi myenb zyrug Qiaj Lo Eei kxvq naaiq teij waag Buaj i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb. ninb Bua kxvq,
27.23: “+‘haiq taub pweij ninb Eei maab tiaq, uaq taub zu'g zyruj a'q.’ “zwavj pc'g fivj zyrug kxvq, ‘aa-men.’
27.6: meib Bua xij zu'g lovg maiq zu'g Jiaj Eei la'pyeiq Zeij zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Eei ziab txvb, yaag zx'q fovg hxg puaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq an uaq nxm ziab txvb.
27.2: meib Bua Jiaj Jx-Dcn Daaib pia'g zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Jiu pun meib Bua Eei teib puv uaq Nxi, xij zu'g lyepg ziaj nxm tomb la'pyeiq ton Jyenq, lovg Wi wrtg Jyenq.
27.20: “haiq taub pweij tia Eei auq, uaq taub zu'g zyruj a'q, weig zu'g ninb paaig zu'g ninb Eei tia.” “zwavj pc'g fivj zyrug kxvq, ‘aa-men.’
27.24: “+‘haiq taub pivj Jyenq taij myenb, uaq taub zu'g zyruj a'q.’ “zwavj pc'g fivj zyrug kxvq, ‘aa-men.’
27.7: yaag xij zu'g yem uaq fovg hxg ziag weig Jiu Tov Eei ka'naaiq, yem zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Eei Ra'Myen Fyenb yrub Eei Eang.
27.19: “+‘haiq taub zruj pun kanb fivj myenb, fai kub hanb fu'Jweiq fai aub kwaaq maiq tu'q pcvb fim Eei leid, uaq taub zu'g zyruj a'q.’ “zwavj pc'g fivj zyrug kxvq, ‘aa-men.’
27.17: “+‘haiq taub swiq Jwavg laavd myenb Eei Daub teig kapg Genj zruj Javb hog Eei tovg, uaq taub zu'g zyruj a'q.’ “zwavj pc'g fivj zyrug kxvq, ‘aa-men.’
27.11: tovb uaq Nxi mo-se cvj kxvq Buaj pc'g fivj,
27.5: yem uaq xij zu'g lovg la'pyeiq weig zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Zeij nxm ziab txvb. maiq tuvq lovg Lia'q Eei Jaab sig zu'g naaiq teij la'pyeiq.
27.9: mo-se Zauj zruj sai Eei le-wi myenb kxvq Buaj i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb, “o i-saa-laa-en myenb aag, xij zu'g sekg sekq Eei mwavj lovj. ib Nxi meib Bua penj zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Eei pc'g fivj.
27.16: “+‘haiq taub maiq Tovj nimg ninb Eei tiaj maag, uaq taub zu'g zyruj a'q.’ “zwavj pc'g fivj zyrug kxvq, ‘aa-men.’
27.4: meib Bua Jiaj Jx-Dcn Daaib mivb uaq zang, xij zu'g yem e-Baan Bov ziuj yia ib Nxi Buaj meib Bua Eei waag lyepg naaiq teij la'pyeiq yaag zx'q Wi wrtg Jyenq.
27.10: weig naaiq meib Bua xij zu'g mwavj zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Eei waag yaag ei Jyenq ninb Eei leib latg Zauj livg, tovb yia ib Nxi Jiu pun meib Bua Eei leid.”
27.22: “+‘haiq taub pweij ninb Eei txg fai muag, maiq kunq ninb Eei tia Eei sia'q fai ninb Eei maa Eei sia'q, uaq taub zu'g zyruj a'q.’ “zwavj pc'g fivj zyrug kxvq, ‘aa-men.’
27.12: “meib Bua Jiaj Jx-Dcn Daaib mivb uaq zang, naaiq teij Ju'q fivj myenb, se si-me-on, le-wi, yu-Daa, itg-saaj-Kaa, yo-sepq, Zauj Ben-yaa-min fivj, xij zu'g sruq Jyenq ke-li-sim Bov pwav waag pun pc'g fivj.
27.15: “+‘ta'faanb zavg myenb Eei puab taub zruj taaib Eei miub favj, maiq kunq tiu taaib fai toj taaib Eei favj, se zyruq yruj haig Eei ka'naaiq. haiq taub lyepg taaib pivj Jyenq Bweid Eei txvj, uaq taub zu'g zyruj a'q.’ “zwavj pc'g fivj zyrug kxvq, ‘ aa-men.’
27.13: cvj maaib naaiq teij Ju'q fivj, se lu-Ben, kaatg, aa-se, sej-Bu-lun, Daan Zauj napq-Taa-li, xij zu'g sruq Jyenq e-Baan Bov zunb zyruj Eei waag.
27.1: mo-se Zauj i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei zwavj myenb koj hatg pc'g fivj. ninb Bua kxvq, “meib Bua xij zu'g ei Revg ib Nxi yia Buaj meib Bua Eei yetg zuvq livg.
27.26: “+‘haiq taub maiq kruj lovj Tinb huvb Eei leib latg, se ninb maiq ei Jyenq leib latg zruj, uaq taub zu'g zyruj a'q.’ “zwavj pc'g fivj zyrug kxvq, ‘aa-men.’
27.25: “+‘haiq taub zipq Eaanb Mwavj taij maiq zruj txvg Eei myenb, uaq taub zu'g zyruj a'q.’ “zwavj pc'g fivj zyrug kxvq, ‘aa-men.’

11.18: meib Bua xij zu'g zx'q yia naaiq teij waag zaavb Jyenq Hruq, fapq Jyenq meib Bua Eei Ba'Riu. cvj zx'q naaiq teij waag Kru Jyenq puad yaag Eatq Jyenq pyxvb zruj Javb hog.

11.3: meib Bua xij zu'g Javj Jyenq zyruq yem i-yipq teib puv zruj Eei Javb hog, tovb ninb zruj pun i-yipq huvb, faa-lo, Zauj ninb Eei teib puv Eei yetg zuvq sig.
