11.21: weig pun meib Bua Zauj meib Bua Eei zeib fun Eei Nxib Eia'g yem zyruq hruq Jyenq lcvd pun meib Bua Eei ovb Taaij Eei teib puv zyrug tu'q Eutg zeiq Daauq Dovg luvb yem Daub peib kub vwaaig laub.
11.14: ninb zyrug ziuj zyavb hog pun luvb twib Byuvg yuvd meib Bua Eei Dau, pun Zyrub ken Byuvg Zauj Zunb ken Byuvg weig pun meib Bua tu'q syru laavb zi'g, syavb a'vung tiuq Zauj ka'lanq yrub.
11.23: zyruq zyrug yem meib Bua Eei uaq Daavg mcvj zung Zwrtq uaq teij fivb fivj myenb. meib Bua yaag Zaavq tu'q kaub Lo kaub henq meib Bua uaq teij fivj Eei teib puv.
11.6: yaag xij zu'g Javj Jyenq ninb Navq haiq nx zruj pun lu-Ben Eei fun, e-li-apg Eei txn, Daa-Taan Zauj aa-Bi-lam. yem i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb Bu'Dovj Dau Gxi Navq mxvj Gxi Rwib, na'q ninb Bua Zauj ninb Bua Eei pyauq zov myenb, lyemb Dopg liub Zauj yetg zuvq maaib mcvg Eei ka'naaiq.
11.2: meib Bua ib Nxi xij zu'g Javj Jyenq zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Navq haiq nx Bx'q Faauj meib Bua. yia maiq zeid Zauj meib Bua Eei fu'Jweiq kxvq weig zu'g ninb Bua maiq hiuq yaag maiq tu'q pwatg zyruq Dovg haaij Lo, Dovg haaij henq, Dovg haaij maaib Qa'q.
11.20: yaag xij zu'g fiaq Jyenq meib Bua Eei pyauq Eei kcvb zrug Zauj meib Bua Eei laatg kcvb,
11.24: ta'faanb meib Bua Eei zauj Zaaiq Tauj haaij, uaq nxm txvj zyrug penj meib Bua Eei Revg a'q. meib Bua Eei kapg Jaaij yem naamb puv Eei teib puvb Waav mivb pa'q puv Tauj le-Baa-nxn keb, cvj yem tov puv yu-fe-titg Daaib mivb Tauj fai puv Eei me-Di-te-le-nyen Kxiq.
11.28: sij kxvq meib Bua maiq ei zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Eei leib latg, kwavg Jyenq yia ib Nxi hatg meib Bua Eei leid, mivb zavg kanb taub zyenb, tovb meib Bua maiq hiuq Eei zyenb, meib Bua zyrug zu'g syrug naaiq teij zyruj Eei waag.
11.7: se meib Bua kanb Eei mziv tu'q pwatg Jyenq zyruq zruj Eei naaiq teij yetg zuvq Lo haig Eei sig.
11.29: zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, txb meib Bua pia'g xij penj meib Bua Eei pwrng uaq nxm teib puv uaq zang, xij zu'g yem ke-li-sim Bov zunb uaq teij pwav Eei waag, yaag yem e-Baan Bov zunb uaq teij zyruj Eei waag.
11.19: xij zu'g Faauj meib Bua Eei fu'Jweiq hiuq tu'q naaiq teij waag. maiq kunq yem pyauq fai yem Jauq zavg, pweij Fiag fai Jiad sin, zuvq xij zu'g pwib Jyenq yem.
11.17: sij kxvq Navq naaig, zyruq zyrug Qiaj Jiad haig meib Bua, pun luvb haand, maiq twib Byuvg. Dau yaag maiq Zwrtq kcvb zwavj. maiq laub meib Bua zu'g myetg, maiq tu'q yem zyruq xij Jiu pun meib Bua uaq nxm lovj haig Eei teib puv.
11.31: meib Bua xij zu'g Jiaj Jx-Dcn Daaib pia'g mivb Zaavq zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Jiu pun meib Bua weig penj meib Bua Eei pwrng teib puv. meib Bua tu'q taaib cvj yem Jyenq Eei zyavb hog,
11.30: meib Bua hiuq tu'q naaiq teij i nxm Bov yem uaq vaang zi'g Jx-Dcn Daaib, mivb fai puv, Ba'Nxi Dxtq mcvj Eei Jauq, yem Kaa-naa-an myenb Eei aa-laa-Baa teig, kin-kaan txib vaang, nitq mo-le Eei tomb Ba'ov zwei Dyavb lomg.
11.27: sij kxvq meib Bua ei Jyenq zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Eei leib latg, meib Bua zyrug tu'q ziuj uaq teij pwav Eei waag.
11.11: mq paag meib Bua xij Jiaj mivb tu'q pia'g uaq nxm teib puv maaib Bov, maaib hxvd, yaag maaib Byuvb uam yuvd.
11.5: xij zu'g Javj Jyenq yem teib puvb Waav ninb Navq haiq nx Tevj meib Bua Zivj tu'q Tauj naaiq nxm txvj.
11.9: yaag pun meib Bua yem zyruq hruq pun meib Bua Eei ovb Taaij Zauj ninb Bua Eei zeib fun Eei teib puv zyavb tu'q syrug Ewrnb Daauq. se yetg nxm Daub Truq lovj Eei teib puv
11.16: xij zu'g faij fim, maiq tuvq zu'g Duaq leib zyruq, mivb fub suj kanb taub zyenb.
11.4: xij zu'g Javj Tauj ninb Navq haiq nx zruj pun i-yipq Eei pcv Zauj ninb Bua Eei maad Zauj Bx'q Jaaj Eei maab Zia, tovb ninb Bua zung meib Bua uaq zang, zyruq pun Kxib si'q Eei uam yemj, myetg Revg ninb Bua.
11.10: meib Bua xij pia'g mivb Ripg Eei teib puv se maiq Navq meib Bua Zwrtq taaib Eei i-yipq teib puv. yem i-yipq meib Bua zwavj ka'naaib Eim yaag xij zu'g lovg zauj Damg Ziab yenb Zia uam yuvd lai Navq yuvd laib Wivj nx.
11.22: sij kxvq meib Bua lovb lovj Eei kan yia Jiu pun meib Bua naaiq teij yetg zuvq leid, se meib Bua Namq zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, yavb ninb Eei tob leid yaag Kauj wrnq ninb,
11.12: se zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, ziuj kruj Eei teib puv. zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Eei mziv zanb zang mavg Jyenq yem Havb taaub Tauj Havb mweid.
11.15: meib Bua kanb tu'q Eang peuq. ninb yaag pun miaq Zwrtq weig meib Bua Eei scvb Kuq Eang.
11.13: sij kxvq meib Bua ei Jyenq yia ib Nxi Jiu pun meib Bua Eei leid, se Namq zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb yaag lovg Revg Hruq, lovg Revg za'eij fub suj ninb.
11.1: xij zu'g Namq zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, zanb zang ei Jyenq ninb hatg Eei waag, ninb Eei leib latg Zauj livg Zauj tiub tiub leid.
11.26: mavg maa'b! ib Nxi yia txb pwav Eei waag Zauj zyruj Eei waag pun meib Bua Namq mavg kaaj.
11.25: maiq maaib haiq taub nxig tu'q meib Bua. zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, ziuj ninb lcvd Eei waag xij pun meib Bua Zaaiq tu'q Tauj Eei txvj Eei myenb kamb Riaj haig, Bua'g hxvb meib Bua.

5.8: “maiq tuvq weig kanb zruj haiq Euvg miub favj, maiq kunq yem kub vwaaig luvb, yem ka'Diaq Dau fai yem Daub Diaq Eei uam ka'Euad haiq Euvg Eei favj.
5.33: xij zu'g ei Jyenq zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Buaj Eei naaiq teij tiub tiub leid zruj, meib Bua zyrug tu'q zyavb Jyenq, tu'q lovj, yaag tu'q yem meib Bua xij Ripg Eei teib puv laub.
5.3: naaiq teij vcvg waag zyruq maiq taan Zauj Bua Eei ovb Taaij Bua lyepg Navq, yaag Zauj Bua, tovb ib Nxi zyavb Jyenq yem naaiq Eei zwavj myenb lyepg.
5.32: i-saa-laa-en myenb aag, meib Bua xij zu'g lovg Hruq ei Jyenq zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, hatg meib Bua Eei waag. yaag maiq tuvq puvj Dxtq yetg tiub.
5.21: “maiq tuvq mauq myenb Eei auq. yaag maiq tuvq mweig Jia'q myenb Eei pyauq fai livb teig, ninb Eei nrub kauq nrub peid, ninb Eei vovb fai lxb, fai ninb maaib Eei haiq Euvg ka'naaiq.”
5.14: mq paag ta'Zyetq Nxi se tivb kov Nxi weig fuvj pun zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb. uaq Nxi maiq tuvq zruj haiq Euvg kov. meib Bua kanb Zauj meib Bua Eei naamb Erud, meib Bua Eei nrub kauq nrub peid, meib Bua Eei vovb, meib Bua Eei lxb, fai meib Bua Eei haiq Euvg scvb Kuq, fai yem meib Bua Eei zivb Eei kanb fivj myenb, maiq tuvq zruj haiq Euvg kov, weig pun meib Bua Eei nrub kauq nrub peid tu'q Zauj meib Bua fib Navq Eei hitq Kwrnj.
5.23: meib Bua haid kxvq waag Eei Qiaj yem Mwavj ka'Euad Zwrtq, yaag pwatg trud zia'g Jyenq Bov Eei zyavb hog, meib Bua fivb fivj Eei pyeiq zeiq Zauj myenb koj taaib lxd yia
5.6: “yia se zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, tovb txb meib Bua Zwrtq i-yipq teib puv zruj nrub Eei txvj.
5.2: zyruq, Bua Eei Tinb huvb, yem ho-lepq Bov Zauj Bua lyepg Jiad vcvg waag.
5.20: “maiq tuvq zruj Jaaq zxvb zevj hxig myenb.
5.24: zyrug kxvq, “mavg maa'b! zyruq, Bua Eei Tinb huvb, hing ninb Eei Favb laavg pun Bua tu'q pwatg yaag piuj mevb ninb Eei Favb laavg Zauj Qa'q. Bua haid ninb Eei Qiaj yem trud ka'Euad kxvq Zwrtq. ib Nxi Bua pwatg Tinb huvb Zauj myenb kxvq waag, myenb Zxg tu'q zyavb Jyenq Eei.
5.28: meib Bua Zauj yia kxvq waag uaq zang zyruq haid mig a'q. zyruq kxvq Buaj yia, “yia haid naaiq teij myenb Zauj meib kxvq Eei waag. ninb Bua kxvq Eei waag se hxpg Eei.
5.7: “Zwrtq liud yia, maiq tuvq zavg kanb taub zyenb.
5.29: o feij tu'q ninb Bua zanb zang maaib Hruq Navq naaig nx. ninb Bua zyrug Taaib yia, ei Jyenq yia Eei yetg zuvq leib latg, weig pun ninb Bua Zauj ninb Bua Eei fu'Jweiq funb fa'q yetg liud tu'q lovj.
5.31: mq paag meib kanb Zauj yia yem naaiq. yia xij zx'q yetg zuvq leib latg Zauj livg Zauj leid Jiu pun meib. meib xij zu'g Faauj ninb Bua, pun ninb Bua yem yia xij Jiu pun ninb Bua Ripg Eei teib puv ei Jyenq zruj.”
5.30: “meib xij zu'g mivb Buaj ninb Bua Rwrnj kanb Eei Dopg liub a'q.
5.27: mo-se aag, Toq meib mivb fatq mwavj zyruq, Bua Eei Tinb huvb, kxvq Eei yetg zuvq waag. cvj txb zyruq, Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Zauj meib kxvq uaq teij waag Rwrnj taaib Buaj yia Bua, yia Bua zyrug mwavj yaag ei Jyenq zruj.”
5.11: “maiq tuvq la'kwaib lovg zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb Eei Buaj. haiq taub la'kwaib lovg zyruq Eei Buaj, zyruq xij tivg uaq taub Eei zwid.
5.5: uaq zang yia sruq Jyenq zyruq Zauj meib Bua Bu'Dovj, zunb zyruq Eei waag pun meib Bua mwavj, weig zu'g meib Bua kamb Riaj trud zyrug maiq faauj Bov. zyruq kxvq,
5.9: maiq tuvq kweig Fiag paaij naaiq teij miub favj yaag maiq tuvq zavg, weig zu'g yia, zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Rcv Jyenq meib Bua. yia xij tivg Rxv yia uaq teij myenb Eei zwid, tivg Tauj ninb Bua Eei pua pyei txig zeib fun.
5.16: “xij zu'g Tovj nimg meib Bua Eei tiaj maag ziuj zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, hatg Eei waag, weig pun meib Bua zyavb tu'q syrug Ewrnb Daauq yaag tu'q lovj yem zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Jiu pun meib Bua Eei teib puv.
5.4: zyruq yem Bov kub vwaaig, trud ka'Euad, Zauj meib Bua Myen txij Myen kxvq waag.
5.10: haiq taub Namq yia, ei Jyenq yia Eei leib latg zruj, yia zyrug Namq ninb Jiaj mivb Tauj yetg Zin txig.
5.22: naaiq teij leib latg se zyruq yem Bov kub vwaaig, yem trud Zauj Bwrnj Zauj om Jyenq Mwavj Eei txvj ka'Euad, lovg Qiaj Lo Eei kxvq Buaj kapq zunq Eei zwavj myenb. ninb yaag maiq Tipq haiq Euvg waag. Ga'haaq ninb zx'q naaiq teij leib latg fiaq Jyenq i Kwaaiq la'pyeib penq Jiu pun yia.
5.12: “xij zu'g ziuj zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, hatg Eei waag syru tivb kov Nxi penj Zivb Revg Nxi.
5.15: xij zu'g Javj Jyenq meib Bua yem i-yipq teib puv zruj Jiaj nrub, zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, suv henq haig Eei puad, lovg tomb Qa'q txb meib Bua Zwrtq taaib. weig naaiq zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, hatg meib Bua syru tivb kov Nxi.
5.13: maaib Ju'q Nxi zruj meib Bua Eei yetg zuvq kov,
5.1: mo-se heug i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb taaib zunq zyrug kxvq, “o i-saa-laa-en myenb aag, mwavj lovj yia ib Nxi xij kxvq Buaj meib Bua Eei leib latg Zauj leid. xij zu'g ho'g ling yaag lovg Hruq ei Jyenq zruj.
5.26: weig zu'g maaib haiq taub paamb myenb haid Jiaj zyavb Jyenq Eei Tinb huvb Eei Qiaj yem trud kxvq Zwrtq Navq Bua haid nx, Zxg maaib mcvg zyavb Jyenq Eei fai?
5.25: mq paag ib zang Bua weig haiq tiug xij zu'g taig? naaiq kwaaj kamb Riaj Eei trud xij puaq myetg Bua. sij kxvq Bua cvj haid zyruq, Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Eei Qiaj kaub laub, Bua zyrug taig a'q.

9.18: yia cvj Baapq Fiag zyruq Eei Ra'Myen Navq zinb Daavg uaq Rung nx. feij zyepg Nxi feij zyepg mwrnd yia maiq Eang Naavj, maiq hopq uam, laaij meib Bua paamd Eei yetg zuvq zwid, se ziuj zyruq pwatg meib Bua zruj x'q haig Eei sig Zua'q ninb Qiaj Jiad.
9.8: lyemb yem ho-lepq Bov meib Bua Zua'q zyruq Qiaj Jiad, ninb zyrug nrud haig meib Bua, zuvq xij myetg Revg meib Bua.
9.3: mq paag ib Nxi meib Bua xij zu'g hiuq tu'q se zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, yem meib Bua Eei uaq Daavg mcvj Navq trud puaq Qwi Revg. zyruq xij myetg ninb Bua, pun ninb Bua yem meib Bua Eei Ra'Myen zu'g swei. Navq naaig, meib Bua zyrug zung ninb Bua Zwrtq, syepg syepq Eei myetg Revg ninb Bua, Navq zyruq Zauj meib Bua lcvd Eei waag.
9.21: yia zx'q meib Bua paamd zwid toj taaib uaq taub vovb txn lovg trud puaq. puaq liud, yia cvj Bx'q huq, mxg penj Bwrnq Navq niab Buv nx, zyrug haad yem Bov lyrug Fiag Eei Do'q.
9.14: maiq tuvq laanb yia. yia xij myetg ninb Bua, pun yem naaiq luvb Diaq maiq maaib haiq taub Javj tu'q ninb Bua Eei Buaj. yia zyrug pun meib zruj yetg fivj kaub Lo kaub henq ninb Bua.”
9.23: zyruq heug meib Bua Zwrtq Kaa-Detg-Baa-nia uaq zang ninb kxvq, “pia'g mivb zx'q yia Jiu pun penj meib Bua Eei pwrng uaq nxm teib puv.” mq paag meib Bua vcvg Jyenq zyruq hatg Eei waag, maiq syenj ninb, maiq mwavj ninb Eei waag.
9.6: Navq naaig, meib Bua xij zu'g hiuq tu'q zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, zx'q naaiq nxm lovj Eei teib puv Jiu pun meib Bua, penj meib Bua Eei pwrng, se maiq zeid weig meib Bua zruj tu'q hxpg, weig zu'g meib Bua penj yetg fivj Hruq vcvg Eei myenb.
9.2: yem uaq Eei myenb yrug Lo yrug Lav, se aa-naakq myenb Eei zeib fun. meib Bua hiuq tu'q Tauj naaiq teij myenb yaag haid myenb kxvq Jiaj, “haiq taub haib vcvg tu'q aa-naakq myenb?”
9.20: zyruq yaag Qiaj Jiad haig aa-lon, xij myetg ninb, mq paag uaq zang yia yaag weig ninb tauj kauj.
9.24: yem yia hiuq tu'q meib Bua uaq Nxi Tauj ib zang meib Bua Kuvj vcvg zyruq Navq.
9.28: maiq zei c'q, meib txb yia Bua Zwrtq uaq nxm teib puv Eei myenb xij kxvq, ‘zyruq maiq maaib panb zeig txb naaiq teij pc'g fivj pia'g ninb lcvd Jiu pun ninb Bua Eei teib puv. zyruq yaag Rxv ninb Bua Zivj taaib txb ninb Bua Zwrtq mivb yem teib puvb Waav taij taig ninb Bua.’
9.7: xij zu'g Javj Jyenq, maiq tuvq la'Ku'q, yem teib puvb Waav meib Bua Navq haiq nx Zua'q zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Qiaj Jiad. yem meib Bua Zwrtq i-yipq teib puv uaq Nxi taaib Tauj naaiq nxm txvj, meib Bua vcvg zyruq.
9.29: mq paag ninb Bua se meib Eei pc'g fivj, meib kanb Eei myenb, tovb meib lovg meib Eei tomb Qa'q Zauj meib henq haig Eei puad txb Zwrtq taaib.”
9.19: yia kamb Riaj haig  zyruq Dovg naaig nrud, Qiaj Jiad haig meib Bua, zuvq xij myetg meib Bua. mq paag zyruq cvj mwavj Rung yia Toq Eei waag.
9.17: yia zyrug zx'q yem yia Eei i Jia'q puad uaq teij i Kwaaiq la'pyeiq ma'g Fiag meib Bua Eei Ra'Myen huq Revg.
9.27: Toq Javj Jyenq meib Eei pru, apg-laa-ham, i-sakg Zauj yaa-Kopq. maiq tuvq Yetq Hruq naaiq teij myenb Hruq vcvg, zruj waaig sig, paamd zwid.
9.11: Jiaj liud feij zyepg Nxi feij zyepg mwrnd, zyruq zx'q naaiq teij i Kwaaiq la'pyeib penq Jiu pun yia, se fiaq Jyenq vcvg waag Eei la'pyeib penq.
9.5: se maiq zeid weig meib Bua zruj tu'q hxpg, fai meib Bua Hruq zivj, zyruq Zivj taaib pun meib Bua Rcv tu'q ninb Bua Eei teib puv penj meib Bua Eei. se laaij uaq teij fivb fivj myenb zruj waaig sig, zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Zivj zung ninb Bua Zwrtq meib Bua Eei uaq Daavg mcvj, yaag weig ei Jyenq ninb Zauj meib Bua Eei ovb Taaij, apg-laa-ham, i-sakg, Zauj yaa-Kopq hruq Eei vcvg waag zruj.
9.9: yia faauj Bov mivb zipq uaq teij la'pyeib penq uaq zang, se maaib zyruq Zauj meib Bua lyepg Eei vcvg waag Eei la'pyeib penq, yia yem uaq Jiaj Bov feij zyepg Nxi feij zyepg mwrnd, maiq Eang Naavj yaag maiq hopq uam.
9.16: yia mavg pwatg meib Bua paamd zwid txvg zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb. meib Bua weig kanb toj vovb txn Eei miub favj, syepg syepq Eei kwavg zyruq hatg meib Bua Eei waag.
9.4: zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, yem meib Bua Eei uaq Daavg mcvj zung Zwrtq uaq teij myenb, maiq tuvq yem Hruq Namq, “zyruq txb yia Bua pia'g taaib tu'q naaiq nxm teib puv weig zu'g yia Bua zruj tu'q hxpg.” zuvq maiq zeid! se laaij uaq teij fivb fivj myenb zruj waaig sig zyruq Zivj zung ninb Bua Zwrtq meib Bua Eei uaq Daavg mcvj.
9.10: zyruq zx'q naaiq teij i Kwaaiq la'pyeib penq pun yia, se lovg ninb kanb Eei puab Do'q fiaq Eei waag. naaiq teij la'pyeib penq fiaq Eei se meib Bua kapq zunq uaq Nxi, zyruq yem Bov kub vwaaig, trud ka'Euad, kxvq Buaj meib Bua Eei yetg zuvq leib latg.
9.22: yem Taa-Be-laa, matq-saaj Zauj Kipg-lotq-hatg-taa-aa-waa meib Bua yaag Zua'q zyruq Qiaj Jiad.
9.12: zyruq Buaj yia, “kaanq Fiag Bov mivb, weig zu'g meib Eei pc'g fivj, tovb meib txb Zwrtq i-yipq teib puv Eei pc'g fivj, zruj waaig sig mig a'q. ninb Bua syepg syepq Eei kwavg yia hatg Eei waag, weig kanb toj miub favj.”
9.15: yia zyrug taauj sin Fiag Bov. Bov Zxg maaib trud zia'g Jyenq Eei. yia Eei i Jia'q puad nanq Jyenq fiaq Jyenq vcvg waag uaq teij i Kwaaiq la'pyeib penq.
9.13: zyruq cvj kxvq Buaj yia, “yia pwatg naaiq teij myenb za'kevb! Hruq vcvg Eei myenb.
9.1: i-saa-laa-en myenb aag, mwavj lovj og. meib Bua ib Nxi xij Jiaj Jx-Dcn Daaib pia'g mivb zung Zwrtq kaub Lo, kaub henq meib Bua uaq teij kua'q Eei myenb. ninb Bua Eei zivb yrug Lo yrug wrnq, zivb laatg Bcvg luvb Lav.
9.26: yia tauj kauj Toq zyruq, “o zyruq Tinb huvb aa'b! maiq tuvq myetg meib Eei pc'g fivj, se meib kanb Eei pc'g fivj, tovb meib lovg tomb Qa'q zua'g ninb Bua, txb ninb Bua Zwrtq i-yipq teib puv taaib Eei myenb.
9.25: uaq teij feij zyepg Nxi feij zyepg mwrnd yia Baapq Fiag yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen weig zu'g zyruq kxvq ninb xij myetg meib Bua.

16.18: meib Bua xij zu'g yem zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Jiu pun meib Bua Eei nxmb nxm zivb, ziuj meib Bua Eei fivb fivj myenb xn teij myenb zruj syemq zwid Jyen Zauj kunq sig Jyen. ninb Bua zyrug haib pcvb fim Eei syemq myenb.
16.8: Ju'q Nxi ka'Euad xij zu'g Eang maiq an pivq Eei Fuaq. ta'Zyetq Nxi xij zu'g kapq zunq zruj leib paaij zavg zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, yaag maiq tuvq zruj haiq Euvg kov.
16.3: meib Bua Eang naaiq taub scvb Kuq Eei xq, maiq tuvq Eang an pivq Eei Fuaq Zauj. naaiq teij siag Nxi ka'Euad xij zu'g Eang maiq an pivq Eei Fuaq, se heug tob naang Fuaq, weig zu'g meib Bua kaanq Jyenq pyauj Zwrtq i-yipq teib puv. Navq naaiq meib Bua zyrug yetg seij Javj Jyenq meib Bua Zwrtq i-yipq teib puv Eei zyavb hog.
16.21: meib Bua Zeij zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb Eei ziab txvb, yem ziab txvb ka'Len maiq tuvq lyepg aa-se-laa zyenb Eeid Eei favj.
16.14: Jiaj naaiq nxm zipq xij zu'g Fyenb yrub naug Eitg, meib Bua Zauj meib Bua Eei naamb Erud, meib Bua Eei nrub kauq nrub peid, Zauj yem meib Bua Eei zivb Eei le-wi myenb, Zauj kanb fivj myenb, Zauj kub hanb fu'Jweiq, Zauj aub kwaaq.
16.6: Kuvj xij zu'g yem zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, xij kinq taaib weig lyepg ninb kanb Eei mevb uaq nxm txvj ziag. yem uaq luvb maanb Mwavj, Ba'Nxi Dxtq Eei zyavb hog, se txij Zwrtq i-yipq teib puv Eei zyavb hog, xij zu'g ziag weig siaj mcvg zipq Eei scvb Kuq.

13.13: yem ninb Bua ka'Euad maaib teij myenb waaig myenb Zwrtq taaib yua'g kanb Eei pwrnb zivb myenb. ninb Bua kxvq, “Bua mivb zavg kanb taub zyenb x'g?” (tovb meib Bua maiq hiuq tu'q Eei zyenb).

1.24: ninb Bua zyrug Zwrtq Jauq yavb Bov mivb Tauj etg-Ko hxvd zaab uaq teij Dau.

1.21: mavg maa'b! zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, zx'q naaiq nxm teib puv Jiu pun meib Bua mig a'q. kunq pia'g mivb zx'q naaiq nxm teib puv Navq zyruq, meib Bua Eei ovb Taaij Eei Tinb huvb, Buaj meib Bua uaq nx. maiq tuvq kamb Riaj yaag maiq tuvq Hruq Waav.”

26.5: meib Bua xij zu'g cvj yem zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Eei Ra'Myen Eyemg kxvq, “yia Eei ovb Taaib vc'q se aa-lam myenb. ninb yrub Jyenq mivb Fiag Tauj i-yipq teib puv, yem Jyenq uaq. ninb Eei myenb zo'g Eei. Ga'haaq ninb Bua Yaavj taaib penj yetg fivj Lo Eei, henq Eei, myenb Zamq Eei.
26.16: ib Nxi zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, hatg meib Bua kan Revg naaiq teij leib latg Zauj leid. weig naaiq xij zu'g lovg Revg Hruq, lovg Revg za'eij ei Jyenq zruj.
26.17: ib Nxi meib Bua Eyemg zyruq zruj meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, lcvd yavb ninb Eei tod, ei Jyenq ninb Eei leib latg, Zauj livg, Zauj leid yaag mwavj ninb Eei waag.
26.14: weig myenb taig yia Raub Eyemq Eei zyavb hog yia maiq Eang naaiq teij Zivb Revg ka'naaiq. maaib wij Eei zyavb hog yia maiq txb naaiq Euvg Zivb Revg Eei ka'naaiq Zwrtq pyauq yaag maiq fovg hxg haiq Euvg pun taig mivb Eei myenb. yia mwavj zyruq, yia Eei Tinb huvb, Eei waag, ei Jyenq meib Buaj yia Eei yetg zuvq.
26.4: sai myenb zyrug zipq meib Bua prub Jyenq Eei Daan an Jyenq zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Eei ziag txvb Ra'Myen mcvj.
26.2: yem zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Zeij pun Eei Dau syru taaib Eei Euvb Euvg taaub Txvj Zunb kcv, yetg Euvg zx'q teij, tapq Jyenq Daan. xij zu'g mivb zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, kinq taaib lyepg ninb kanb Eei mevb uaq nxm txvj,
26.6: mq paag i-yipq myenb zruj to'g pun yia Bua, pun yia Bua syrug Kruq, yaag hxig zruj kov Niaq.
26.13: xij zu'g kxvq Buaj zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, “yia yem pyauq zx'q Zwrtq Zivb Revg Eei pwrng ka'naaiq pun le-wi myenb Zauj kanb fivj myenb, kub hanb fu'Jweiq Zauj aub kwaaq ziuj meib hatg Eei waag. meib Eei yetg zuvq leib latg yia maiq vcvg yaag maiq la'Ku'q.
26.12: mrud Rung pwavq pua Havj uaq Havj, se syru zyepg kruq Eei yetg kruq Eei Havj, xij zu'g zx'q Zwrtq meib Bua syru zyavj yetg zuvq Zunb kcv zyepg kruq Eei yetg kruq, pun le-wi myenb, kanb fivj myenb, kub hanb fu'Jweiq Zauj aub kwaaq, weig pun ninb Bua yem meib Bua Eei muvq tu'q Eang peuq.
26.15: Toq zyruq yem kub vwaaig luvb, meib Eei Zivb Revg txvj, mavg Fiag Zeij fu'q pun meib Eei pc'g fivj, i-saa-laa-en myenb, yaag Zeij fu'q pun meib Jiu pun yia Bua Eei teib puv, Navq meib hruq Jyenq Zeij pun yia Bua Eei ovb Taaij uaq nxm Daub Truq lovj Eei teib puv.”
26.11: meib Bua Zauj le-wi myenb Zauj yem meib Bua Bu'Dovj Eei kanb fivj myenb xij zu'g Fyenb yrub xnb lx'g weig zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Zeij pun meib Bua Zauj meib Bua Eei pyauq zov myenb Eei yetg zuvq.
26.1: meib Bua tu'q pia'g mivb yem Jyenq zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Jiu pun meib Bua Ripg Eei teib puv,
26.10: o zyruq aag, ib zang yia txb meib Zeij pun yia Bua Eei Dau Zwrtq Eei taaub Txvj Zunb kcv taaib fovg hxg pun meib.” kxvq liud zyrug zx'q meib Bua Eei Daan an Jyenq zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb Eei Ra'Myen, cvj paaij ninb.

25.18: meib Bua yem Jauq zavg mau haig, Kruq haig uaq zang, ninb Bua Zwrtq taaib tavq Jyenq kan Ga'haaq taaib uaq teij. ninb Bua yaag maiq kamb Riaj Tinb huvb.
25.3: mq paag maiq tuvq pun ninb zu'g Bx'q kaub Zamq feij zyepg pin. sij kxvq Bx'q Jiaj Daavg sruj mrug, Riaj zruj pun meib Bua Eei kxb yrud zaang haig.
25.8: uaq nxm zivb Eei myenb koj zyrug heug uaq taub myenb taaib naaig ninb. sij kxvq ninb Zxg vcvg Jyenq kxvq, “yia maiq xij lovg ninb zruj auq” nx,
25.19: Navq naaig, zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, pun meib Bua tu'q yem Jyenq ninb xij Jiu pun meib Bua Ripg Eei teib puv hitq Kwrnj, maiq zu'g weib kxmj Eei winb wavq hxig. meib Bua xij zu'g taij Revg naaiq teij aa-maa-lekq myenb pun ninb Bua zutg Revg. yem luvb Diaq maiq maaib haiq taub Javj tu'q ninb Bua Eei Buaj. meib Bua Zinb maang maiq tuvq la'Ku'q.
25.9: uaq taub Eaamb kwaaq zyrug txv Jyenq myenb koj mivb Tutq ninb Eei yrud Eei yetg Jia'q heb, yaag Twiq uamb Rwib nctq ninb Eei Myen kxvq, “ta'faanb maiq Tevj ninb Eei kxj Zeij Mwavq txig Eei myenb xij zu'g Navq naaiq nx zruj pun ninb.”
25.7: sij kxvq taig mivb uaq taub Goj Eei muab txig maiq Kavq pun Ripg ninb Eei kxj fai yrud Eei Buaj, uaq taub auq zyrug mivb zivb kcvb, myenb koj uaq kxvq, “yia Eei Goj Eei muab txig maiq Kavq pun ninb Eei kxj Eei Buaj yem i-saa-laa-en myenb Bu'Dovj Ripg Jyenq mivb. ninb maiq Kavq ei Jyenq lovg Eaamb kwaaq Eei leib Eeig lovg yia zruj auq.”
25.5: sij kxvq maaib i muab txn Jwavg pyauq yem, maaib taub taig mig a'q, yaag maiq kcvb maaib txn, taig uaq taub Eei auq maiq tu'q Zwrtq kcvb mivb lovg ka'Eiag Eei myenb zruj Goj. Goj Eei kxj fai yrud xij zu'g ei Jyenq lovg Eaamb kwaaq fai Riab kwaaq Eei leib Eeig lovg ninb zruj auq.
25.16: weig zu'g zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, yruj haig zruj naaiq Euvg sig Eei myenb, se Hruq Fwrtq, Hruq Pyen Eei myenb.
25.17: xij zu'g Javj Jyenq meib Bua Zwrtq i-yipq teib puv yem Jauq zavg uaq zang aa-maa-lekq myenb Navq haiq nx zruj pun meib Bua.
25.14: yem meib Bua Eei pyauq yaag maiq tuvq maaib i Euvg Laau Eei ka'naaiq, yetg nxm Lo, yetg nxm faij.
25.4: vovb ling Byaub Eei zyavb hog maiq tuvq tru vovb Eei Rwib pcvj.
25.2: sij kxvq maaib zwid uaq taub zig tu'q Bx'q, syemq zwid Jyen zyrug heug ninb Baapq Fiag Dau, ziuj ninb zruj Eei zwid zig tu'q Bx'q Eei sruj mrug txv Jyenq syemq zwid Jyen zu'g Bx'q.
25.6: ninb yuvd tu'q taaub taub txn xij zu'g Ripg taig uaq taub kxj fai yrud Eei Buaj weig maiq pun ninb Eei Buaj yem i-saa-laa-en myenb Bu'Dovj zutg Revg.
25.13: maiq tuvq maaib i Euvg Ryavb txb, yetg nxm Lo yetg nxm faij, tapq Jyenq meib Bua Eei Bua'g.
25.12: meib Bua xij zu'g Va'q Dutq uaq taub auq Eei puad. yaag maiq tuvq Kxb lyenb ninb.
25.15: Ryav Eei Zauj Laau Eei ka'naaiq xij zu'g hxpg Eei, txij Eei. Navq naaig meib Bua zyrug yem zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Jiu pun meib Bua Eei teib puv zyavb tu'q syrug Ewrnb Daauq,
25.11: sij kxvq maaib i taub myenb Bx'q Jaaj, maaib yetg taub Eei auq xij mivb Fruj ninb Eei Goj pyauj Dutq Bx'q ninb Eei Goj uaq taub, zyrug suv puad Eau Jyenq uaq taub myenb Eei lamb Bweid txvj,
25.1: sij kxvq i taub myenb maaib sig pcv Tauj sig txvb, syemq zwid Jyen zyrug tivg haiq taub txvg, haiq taub maiq txvg.
25.10: yem i-saa-laa-en myenb Bu'Dovj uaq pwrng myenb zyrug tu'q Buaj heug “zu'g Tutq heb Eei Mwavq txig.”
